Dialogue: 0.0:00:03.33.0:00:05.61.Default..0.0.0..ME AND VINNY ARE HAVING\NA REALLY GOOD TIME RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:05.63.0:00:07.98.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE HE'S STARTING TO FEEL\NWHAT I'VE BEEN FEELING.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:08.00.0:00:09.81.Default..0.0.0..COME TO YOUR BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:09.84.0:00:11.08.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:11.11.0:00:13.15.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN HE WANTS\NNOTHING TO DO WITH ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.18.0:00:14.42.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. MAKE UP YOUR MIND.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:14.44.0:00:15.82.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE CALL A CAB\NREALLY QUICK?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:15.85.0:00:17.59.Default..0.0.0..I'LL CALL A CAB FOR YOU.\NAWW. MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:17.61.0:00:19.52.Default..0.0.0..IT'S A SURPRISE; WE'RE GONNA\NTAKE THEM TO TIMES SQUARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:19.55.0:00:21.79.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE NOT GOING TO JENK'S.\NYOU'RE GOING TO TIMES SQUARE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:21.82.0:00:23.46.Default..0.0.0..IS THAT NEW YORK CITY?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:23.49.0:00:24.70.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. YOU KNOW-\NWHERE ARE WE GOING?!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.72.0:00:25.70.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS A GOOD PRANK.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:25.72.0:00:27.83.Default..0.0.0..WE NEED TO GET HIM BACK\NSOMEHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:27.86.0:00:29.50.Default..0.0.0..I'M LEAVING MY HOME\NRIGHT NOW
Dialogue: 0.0:00:29.53.0:00:32.20.Default..0.0.0..TO GO BACK INTO THE MADNESS\NAT THE JERSEY SHORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:32.23.0:00:33.31.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M THINKING TO MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:33.33.0:00:35.11.Default..0.0.0.."YOU'RE READY.\NYOU CAN DO THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.13.0:00:39.51.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW WHO YOU ARE. SAM.\NYOU'RE GONNA BE FINE."
Dialogue: 0.0:00:39.54.0:00:41.68.Default..0.0.0..DJ PAULY DELVECCHIO!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.70.0:00:44.18.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING TO THE JERSEY SHORE.\NBITCH!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:44.21.0:00:46.75.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NWE GOT A SITUATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:46.78.0:00:48.52.Default..0.0.0..I'M THE SWEETEST BITCH\NYOU'LL EVER MEET.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:50.81.0:00:53.49.Default..0.0.0..AFTER I HAVE SEX WITH A GUY.\NI WILL RIP THEIR HEADS OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:53.52.0:00:55.43.Default..0.0.0..GO VINNY! GO VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:55.45.0:00:57.72.Default..0.0.0..YOU LIKE THE BOOBS?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.53.0:01:05.37.Default..0.0.0..SNOOK. LOOK WHAT\NI GOT YOU. THOUGH. SNOOK.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:05.39.0:01:06.37.Default..0.0.0..PICKLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.40.0:01:07.51.Default..0.0.0..NOPE. SOMETHING BETTER\NTHAN THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:07.53.0:01:09.30.Default..0.0.0..SOME MOTHERFUCKIN'\NRON RON JUICE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:16.91.0:01:18.88.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I'M FREAKING OUT\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:18.91.0:01:20.32.Default..0.0.0..I AM SO ANXIOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:20.34.0:01:21.49.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW\NIF THESE PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0.0:01:21.51.0:01:22.89.Default..0.0.0..ARE GONNA WANT ME\NBACK IN THE HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:22.91.0:01:25.09.Default..0.0.0..I'M NERVOUS TO SEE RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:25.11.0:01:27.33.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I DON'T KNOW HOW-\NWHAT'S GONNA HAPPEN WITH THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:27.35.0:01:28.33.Default..0.0.0..I JUST THINK I'M A BALL OF.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.35.0:01:29.56.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DIFFERENT EMOTIONS\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:29.59.0:01:31.90.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE MAKING THAT\NWITH PATRON?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:31.92.0:01:33.37.Default..0.0.0..YOU REALLY ARE A PATRON.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:37.89.0:01:39.57.Default..0.0.0..SO WHAT DOES A BABY SUCK ON?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:39.60.0:01:41.21.Default..0.0.0..TIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.23.0:01:44.21.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DOES A BABY\NCALL A BOTTLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.23.0:01:45.34.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DOES IT CALL-\NA BABY CALL A BOTTLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:45.37.0:01:46.98.Default..0.0.0..BABA.\NBABA.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:47.00.0:01:48.51.Default..0.0.0..WHERE DOES PAULY GO\NFOR HIS HAIRCUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.54.0:01:50.15.Default..0.0.0..THE "BABA."\NHI. SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.17.0:01:52.62.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:52.64.0:01:54.29.Default..0.0.0..HI. HON.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:54.31.0:01:56.45.Default..0.0.0..YO. TODAY IS CRAZY!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:56.48.0:01:57.46.Default..0.0.0..HI. SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:57.48.0:01:58.69.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S UP?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:58.71.0:02:00.66.Default..0.0.0..WHEN I HEAR PAULY GO.\N"OH. HEY. SAM."
Dialogue: 0.0:02:00.68.0:02:02.66.Default..0.0.0..I THINK PAULY'S JOKING AROUND.\NLIKE ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:02.69.0:02:05.20.Default..0.0.0..I LOOK UP. AND I'M LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.22.0:02:07.80.Default..0.0.0..HOW ARE YOU? MWAH!\NGOOD. HOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.82.0:02:09.50.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU HAVE A GOOD LI-\NRELIEF?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.53.0:02:11.50.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NFEEL BETTER?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.53.0:02:12.89.Default..0.0.0..MUCH BETTER.\NYOU LOOK GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:17.10.0:02:18.73.Default..0.0.0..AM I DREAMING\NOR AM I AWAKE?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:21.44.0:02:22.75.Default..0.0.0..I DEFINITELY THINK\NIT'D BE NICE
Dialogue: 0.0:02:22.77.0:02:24.55.Default..0.0.0..IF SAM STAYED OUT OF THE HOUSE\NA LITTLE BIT LONGER.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:24.57.0:02:26.82.Default..0.0.0..THINK I WAS JUST STARTING\NTO FIND MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:26.84.0:02:29.19.Default..0.0.0..AND SHE WALKED THROUGH THE DOOR.\NAND I'M JUST LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:29.21.0:02:30.56.Default..0.0.0.."F.M.L."
Dialogue: 0.0:02:30.58.0:02:34.59.Default..0.0.0..I WAS EXPECTING IT.\NBUT I WASN'T EXPECTING IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:34.62.0:02:35.86.Default..0.0.0..HAVE YOU TALKED TO HER\NON THE PHONE?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:35.88.0:02:36.93.Default..0.0.0..TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:36.95.0:02:37.96.Default..0.0.0..AND SHE SAID\NSHE WAS COMING OR NO?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:37.99.0:02:39.23.Default..0.0.0..NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:39.25.0:02:41.47.Default..0.0.0..WHERE ARE THEY ALL?\NLET'S GO SAY HELLO.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:41.49.0:02:43.22.Default..0.0.0..GET DOWN HERE. RIGHT NOW!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:45.29.0:02:47.34.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.36.0:02:49.11.Default..0.0.0..OH. THANK GOD YOU'RE BACK!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.13.0:02:51.44.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU LOOK SO PRETTY.\NOH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.47.0:02:52.81.Default..0.0.0..I'M GONNA CRY.\NI'M SO HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:55.04.0:02:58.38.Default..0.0.0..I. LIKE. WAS SO HA-STATIC\NTHAT I ALMOST CRIED.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:58.41.0:02:59.58.Default..0.0.0..GET OUT OF HERE!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.61.0:03:02.39.Default..0.0.0..HI.\NSAM. YOU LOOK SO PRETTY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:02.41.0:03:04.52.Default..0.0.0..HA-STATIC IS WHEN YOU'RE.\NLIKE. YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.55.0:03:07.53.Default..0.0.0..WHEN YOU'RE. LIKE.\NSUPER HAPPY AND. LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:07.55.0:03:09.63.Default..0.0.0..REALLY HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.65.0:03:12.50.Default..0.0.0..ALL THAT FIGHTING SHIT\NIS DONE. THOUGH. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:12.52.0:03:14.67.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NTSH. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.69.0:03:15.93.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE AN ASSHOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:15.96.0:03:17.64.Default..0.0.0..YO. HONESTLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:17.66.0:03:19.04.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S A COOL GIRL\NAND EVERYTHING. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:19.06.0:03:21.77.Default..0.0.0..THERE WAS NO FIGHTING.\NLET'S KEEP IT THAT WAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.80.0:03:23.04.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT?\NWANT SOME FRIES?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.06.0:03:24.28.Default..0.0.0..WELL. NOT REALLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:25.47.0:03:27.71.Default..0.0.0..GUESS WHAT.\NSAMMI'S BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.84.0:03:30.35.Default..0.0.0..EHH.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.37.0:03:31.75.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW\NSHE WAS GONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.77.0:03:32.92.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T EVEN\NKNOW SHE WAS GONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.94.0:03:34.59.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:34.61.0:03:36.72.Default..0.0.0..WE'LL GO OUT AND DO\NWHAT WE NORMALLY DO. YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:36.75.0:03:38.46.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. WE'LL DO IT ANYWAY.\NYOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN? SO...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:38.48.0:03:42.19.Default..0.0.0..RONNIE'S ACTING. UH.\NLIKE HE'S NOT TOO HAPPY EITHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.22.0:03:44.66.Default..0.0.0..DIDN'T EVEN REALLY SAY\NHELLO TO HER TOO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:44.69.0:03:49.53.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. IT'S BACK TO THE OLD.\NUH. RON AND SAM SAGA.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:49.56.0:03:50.74.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU SEE RON?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.76.0:03:52.14.Default..0.0.0..REALLY. REALLY QUICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:52.16.0:03:53.67.Default..0.0.0..AND...\NHE DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.70.0:03:54.97.Default..0.0.0..JUST SAID HELLO\NAND WALKED AWAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.00.0:03:57.24.Default..0.0.0..I WAS LIKE. "OH. MY GOD."\NSO SINGLE SAMMI OR...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.27.0:03:59.41.Default..0.0.0..YES.\NPROMISE?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.44.0:04:01.11.Default..0.0.0..YES.\NARE YOU HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:01.14.0:04:03.15.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I NEEDED THAT.\NLIKE. REALLY. REALLY BAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:03.17.0:04:05.42.Default..0.0.0..GOOD. YOUR MOOD'S GOOD.\NYOUR NAILS ARE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:05.44.0:04:07.59.Default..0.0.0..MY TOES ARE GOOD.\NMY NAILS ARE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.61.0:04:09.85.Default..0.0.0..I CAN GO GET NAILS DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:09.88.0:04:11.69.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:12.78.0:04:14.53.Default..0.0.0..HI. HOW WE DOIN'. GOOD?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.55.0:04:16.93.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:16.95.0:04:18.96.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK PALE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:18.99.0:04:20.50.Default..0.0.0..ME?\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:20.52.0:04:23.20.Default..0.0.0..UH. I WAS JUST FUCKIN'-\NLIKE. I SAW A GHOST. THAT'S WHY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.50.0:04:28.27.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS SHOCKING FOR YOU\NTO WALK THROUGH THE DOOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.30.0:04:29.31.Default..0.0.0..NOTHING FOR NOTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.33.0:04:31.03.Default..0.0.0..PALE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.47.0:04:41.32.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. NOW THEY'RE\NTELLING SECRETS.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.34.0:04:44.09.Default..0.0.0..HE WAS. LIKE.\NSO DEPRESSED ABOUT YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:44.11.0:04:45.56.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NSO DEPRESSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.58.0:04:48.76.Default..0.0.0..WAS IT REALLY THAT BAD?\NLIKE. HE'S REALLY... THAT BAD?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:48.78.0:04:49.76.Default..0.0.0..NOT A CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.79.0:04:51.06.Default..0.0.0..WE WENT TO KARMA\NTHE OTHER NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:51.09.0:04:52.96.Default..0.0.0..AND WE HAD LIKE A LONG. LIKE.\NDRUNK CONVERSATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.99.0:04:54.37.Default..0.0.0..BUT HE WAS LIKE.\N"I KNOW I WAS WRONG."
Dialogue: 0.0:04:54.39.0:04:56.17.Default..0.0.0..HE WAS LIKE. "I JUST LOST\NTHE BEST THING I EVER HAD."
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.19.0:04:58.67.Default..0.0.0..HE GOES. "I WILL NEVER FIND\NA GIRL LIKE THAT. EVER AGAIN."
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.69.0:05:00.74.Default..0.0.0..SO THE FACT THAT HE KNOWS
Dialogue: 0.0:05:00.76.0:05:02.37.Default..0.0.0..THAT HE'S A DICK\NAND HE FUCKED UP...
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.40.0:05:03.51.Default..0.0.0..HE NEEDS TO GO THROUGH IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.53.0:05:05.44.Default..0.0.0..I'M SOR... I HATE TO SAY IT.\NBUT. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:05.47.0:05:06.91.Default..0.0.0..I'VE BEEN PUT THROUGH\NENOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.94.0:05:09.35.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. MENTALLY AND EMOTIONALLY\NI'VE BEEN DISTRAUGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:09.37.0:05:10.48.Default..0.0.0..WE KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:10.51.0:05:11.58.Default..0.0.0..WE'LL SEE WHAT HAPPENS.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:11.61.0:05:14.52.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. I NEED TO FOCUS\NON MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:14.54.0:05:15.92.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL BAD FOR YOU\NNOW. DOG.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.28.0:05:19.99.Default..0.0.0..I WAS A LITTLE THROWN OFF\NBY THAT FOR A SECOND.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.02.0:05:21.36.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL NO DIFFERENT.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.38.0:05:22.56.Default..0.0.0..OH. GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:22.58.0:05:24.46.Default..0.0.0.."DID HE GO OUT ANYWHERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.49.0:05:27.23.Default..0.0.0..WAS HE TALKING TO A GIRL?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.26.0:05:28.80.Default..0.0.0.."WAIT. DID HE\NGO TO THE GYM?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:28.82.0:05:30.54.Default..0.0.0.."WAS HE TALKING TO A GIRL\NAT THE GYM?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:30.56.0:05:32.47.Default..0.0.0.."NO."\N"DANCING?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:33.53.0:05:36.34.Default..0.0.0.."HE WENT WITH PAULY\NAND VINNY?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:36.37.0:05:37.58.Default..0.0.0.."DID THEY TALK TO GIRLS?'
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.60.0:05:39.61.Default..0.0.0.."THEY WENT TO GET DINNER."
Dialogue: 0.0:05:39.64.0:05:40.71.Default..0.0.0.."DID HE TALK TO GIRLS THERE?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.74.0:05:42.18.Default..0.0.0.."DID HE TALK\NTO THE WAITRESS?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:43.47.0:05:44.75.Default..0.0.0.."DID HE ORDER FOOD?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:44.77.0:05:46.48.Default..0.0.0.."WHAT DID HE ORDER?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:46.51.0:05:48.65.Default..0.0.0.."CAESAR SALAD."\N"WAS THAT WITH CHICKEN?"
Dialogue: 0.0:05:50.31.0:05:51.69.Default..0.0.0..WHAT A FUCKING JOKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:51.71.0:05:54.46.Default..0.0.0..THE JOKE'S ON ME. HUH?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.62.0:05:56.59.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GET READY.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:56.62.0:05:57.76.Default..0.0.0..SO WHAT ARE YOU WEARING?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:57.79.0:05:59.26.Default..0.0.0..WEAR THAT.\NNO. I DON'T LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:05:59.29.0:06:00.33.Default..0.0.0..I'M GONNA DO SOMETHING ELSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:00.36.0:06:02.73.Default..0.0.0..SEXY?\NNO FRICKIN' BOOTY SHORTS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.76.0:06:05.27.Default..0.0.0..DO SOMETHING DRESSY.\NPURPLE DRESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:05.29.0:06:08.01.Default..0.0.0..♪ TAKE TIME ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:06:08.03.0:06:12.71.Default..0.0.0..♪ BUT YOU OUGHT\NTO TAKE BETTER ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.74.0:06:14.58.Default..0.0.0..♪ CARE OF THE SITUATION ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:06:14.60.0:06:16.08.Default..0.0.0..DO I LOOK EMBARRASSING?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:16.11.0:06:17.48.Default..0.0.0..ONLY WHEN YOU WAKE UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:17.51.0:06:19.78.Default..0.0.0..LET'S WALK TO KARMA.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:19.81.0:06:21.25.Default..0.0.0..BABY. YOU'RE MY HAPPINESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:21.28.0:06:22.75.Default..0.0.0..VINNY. I WANNA CUDDLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:22.78.0:06:24.96.Default..0.0.0..WANT ME TO GO OVER THERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:24.98.0:06:28.03.Default..0.0.0..FOR WHAT?\NSNOOKI CALLED. AND I OBEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:28.05.0:06:30.43.Default..0.0.0..HUH?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:30.45.0:06:31.63.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:31.65.0:06:33.76.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA CUDDLE TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:33.79.0:06:35.00.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU REALLY WANT ME TO...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:35.02.0:06:36.63.Default..0.0.0..I UNDERSTAND IF YOU\NSEE A GIRL AT THE CLUB
Dialogue: 0.0:06:36.66.0:06:38.60.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU WANT\NTO BRING HER HOME. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:38.63.0:06:40.41.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU REALLY WANT ME NOT\NTO BRING HOME A GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:40.43.0:06:42.01.Default..0.0.0..TELL ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:42.03.0:06:43.11.Default..0.0.0..I WANT-\NBUT YOU MIGHT... YOU MIGHT...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:43.13.0:06:44.94.Default..0.0.0..YOU MIGHT DO YOUR THING.\NYOU KNOW. SO...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:44.97.0:06:46.21.Default..0.0.0..NAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:46.23.0:06:47.98.Default..0.0.0..OH. I DEFINITELY WANT TO TRY\NAGAIN WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:48.00.0:06:50.25.Default..0.0.0..I ACTUALLY NAMED HIS PENIS\NMOBY DICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:50.27.0:06:53.52.Default..0.0.0..AND I WOULD LOVE TO TRY AGAIN\NTO SEE IF IT WOULD WORK.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:53.54.0:06:54.65.Default..0.0.0..SO MAYBE TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:54.68.0:06:56.78.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA BE WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:58.81.0:07:00.19.Default..0.0.0..GET UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:00.22.0:07:02.63.Default..0.0.0..YO. YOU JUST-\NI'M ANNOYED.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.65.0:07:04.36.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. LET'S TAKE THE SHOT\NSO WE CAN GET IN THE CAB.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:04.39.0:07:06.70.Default..0.0.0..IT'S TIME TO GO.\NTO SAM BEING BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:06.72.0:07:08.73.Default..0.0.0..TO BLOWOUTS. BOOBS...
Dialogue: 0.0:07:08.76.0:07:10.03.Default..0.0.0..TO THE TRIP\NTO NEW YORK CITY!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:11.09.0:07:13.24.Default..0.0.0..YO. CHEERS TO TIMES SQUARE!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:13.26.0:07:14.31.Default..0.0.0..YEAH! TIMES SQUARE!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:14.33.0:07:16.37.Default..0.0.0..TIMES SQUARE!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:16.40.0:07:19.68.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANNA. LIKE.\NSMOTHER YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:19.70.0:07:21.75.Default..0.0.0..THINGS WITH ME AND RONNIE\NARE AWKWARD.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.77.0:07:22.95.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE SUCKING UP TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:22.97.0:07:25.35.Default..0.0.0..RON PRETTY MUCH\NLOOKS LIKE A DOUCHE BAG.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:25.37.0:07:27.45.Default..0.0.0..WE HAVE AN EMERGENCY\NWITH THAT TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:30.85.0:07:32.51.Default..0.0.0..HELP!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:39.52.0:07:44.24.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:07:44.26.0:07:45.64.Default..0.0.0..I MISSED YOU.\NI REALLY DID.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:45.66.0:07:47.91.Default..0.0.0..I MISS YOU TOO.\NI LOVE YOU GUYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:47.93.0:07:49.24.Default..0.0.0..SINGLE LADIES!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:49.26.0:07:50.47.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T HEAR YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:50.50.0:07:51.94.Default..0.0.0..All: SINGLE!\NSINGLE LADIES!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:59.27.0:08:00.79.Default..0.0.0..WHEN SAM COMES OUT\NIN HER NEW BLUE DRESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:00.81.0:08:02.99.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE.\N"GOD. YOU'RE FUCKIN' HOT."
Dialogue: 0.0:08:03.01.0:08:04.42.Default..0.0.0..FUCK ME. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:11.02.0:08:13.02.Default..0.0.0..GOOD. HOW YOU DOIN'?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:14.09.0:08:15.53.Default..0.0.0..WHERE'D THE GUYS GO?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:15.56.0:08:17.57.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T. UH...\NWHAT'S HAPPENIN'?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.59.0:08:18.67.Default..0.0.0..HI.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:18.69.0:08:20.14.Default..0.0.0..SAVE YOUR LIFE?\NHUH?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.16.0:08:21.34.Default..0.0.0..SAVE YOU?\NNO. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:21.36.0:08:22.64.Default..0.0.0..HE'S JUST HANGING OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:22.66.0:08:24.11.Default..0.0.0..WHAT. ARE YOU BY YOURSELF?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:24.13.0:08:26.28.Default..0.0.0..OOH.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:26.30.0:08:28.30.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA BE TAKING JABS\NALL NIGHT. HUH?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.34.0:08:31.98.Default..0.0.0..YOU DO LOOK BEAUTIFUL.\NTHOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.41.0:08:35.29.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE SUCKING UP TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:35.31.0:08:37.59.Default..0.0.0..RON. THIS IS MY\NFIRST NIGHT BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:37.61.0:08:39.66.Default..0.0.0..YOU COULD SAY "YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL"\NALL YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:39.68.0:08:41.33.Default..0.0.0..BUT IT DOESN'T\NCHANGE ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:41.35.0:08:43.33.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. FUCKIN' SUFFER\NFOR A LITTLE BIT MORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:43.35.0:08:44.93.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. COME ON.\NSUFFER.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:44.95.0:08:46.93.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANNA. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:46.96.0:08:49.37.Default..0.0.0..SMOTHER YOU. BUT...\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.39.0:08:51.64.Default..0.0.0..RON PRETTY MUCH\NLOOKS LIKE A DOUCHE BAG.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:51.66.0:08:53.04.Default..0.0.0..SAM WANTS TO HANG OUT\NWITH THE GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.06.0:08:54.41.Default..0.0.0..DO HER OWN THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:54.43.0:08:55.87.Default..0.0.0..AND RON'S JUST LIKE\NA LITTLE PUPPY DOG
Dialogue: 0.0:08:55.90.0:08:59.01.Default..0.0.0..CHASING AFTER THE GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:59.03.0:09:01.21.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S WITH YOU TONIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:01.24.0:09:02.21.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:02.24.0:09:04.82.Default..0.0.0..I'M HAPPY YOU CAME BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:04.84.0:09:07.32.Default..0.0.0..OH. ARE YOU LEAVING?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:07.34.0:09:09.22.Default..0.0.0..NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:09.24.0:09:10.66.Default..0.0.0..WANT ME TO?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.68.0:09:12.81.Default..0.0.0..GO ON. HAVE FUN.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:17.89.0:09:21.00.Default..0.0.0..♪ NEVER THOUGHT\NI'D REGRET YOU ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.02.0:09:23.57.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'D BETTER FORGET ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.59.0:09:26.00.Default..0.0.0..♪ LOVE YOU SINCE\NI MET YOU ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:26.03.0:09:28.24.Default..0.0.0..I THINK IT'S FAIR.\NIF SOMEBODY WANTS THEIR SPACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:28.26.0:09:29.57.Default..0.0.0..YOU GOTTA GIVE IT TO THEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.60.0:09:31.11.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN'T SIT THERE AND...\NCHIP AWAY AT 'EM.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:31.13.0:09:32.48.Default..0.0.0..I JUST DO MY OWN THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:32.50.0:09:33.54.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE HANG OUT\NWITH YOUR FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:33.57.0:09:34.81.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA HOVER\NOVER YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:34.84.0:09:37.82.Default..0.0.0..♪ AND I LOVE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.84.0:09:43.45.Default..0.0.0..♪ ONLY YOU ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.48.0:09:46.19.Default..0.0.0..♪ THROW IT OUT.\NTHROW IT OUT. THROW IT OUT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:46.21.0:09:47.96.Default..0.0.0..♪ THROW IT OUT.\NTHROW IT OUT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.98.0:09:49.03.Default..0.0.0..♪ AHH ♪\N♪ THROW IT OUT. THROW IT OUT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:09:49.05.0:09:51.13.Default..0.0.0..I THINK\NI LIKE VINNY A LOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:51.15.0:09:52.43.Default..0.0.0..WHY WOULDN'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.45.0:09:54.63.Default..0.0.0..IS HE INTO YOU OR NOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.66.0:09:56.47.Default..0.0.0..WANT ME TO FIND OUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.49.0:09:58.94.Default..0.0.0..JUST LEAVE IT ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.96.0:10:00.37.Default..0.0.0..BUT. HEY.\NREALLY THINK. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.40.0:10:01.94.Default..0.0.0..I'M GETTING. LIKE.\NFEELINGS NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.96.0:10:03.47.Default..0.0.0..UH-OH.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.50.0:10:05.24.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW WHAT KIND OF\NMESSAGE VINNY'S SENDING NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.27.0:10:07.38.Default..0.0.0..BUT NICOLE AND VINNY HAVE\NSOME SEXUAL TENSION
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.40.0:10:09.65.Default..0.0.0..THAT THEY NEED TO\NREALLY TALK ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.67.0:10:11.55.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE IT COULD BE DANGEROUS\NTO THE HEALTH.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.57.0:10:14.15.Default..0.0.0..IF HE BRINGS HOME A GIRL.\NI'M GONNA KILL MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.18.0:10:15.49.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S YOUR NAME?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:15.51.0:10:16.65.Default..0.0.0..LAURA.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:16.68.0:10:17.69.Default..0.0.0..LAURA. I'M VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:17.71.0:10:19.02.Default..0.0.0..VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:19.05.0:10:20.46.Default..0.0.0..I'M DOMINICAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.48.0:10:22.33.Default..0.0.0..DOMINICAN?\NALL RIGHT. WELL. WELL. WELL.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:22.35.0:10:23.93.Default..0.0.0..DOMINICAN GIRLS ARE HOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:23.95.0:10:26.30.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE THEY CAN DANCE.\NTHEY CAN MOVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.32.0:10:29.17.Default..0.0.0..THEY GOT TANS.\NTHEY GOT BIG BUTTS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:29.19.0:10:31.17.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. NICE. FULL LIPS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.19.0:10:32.70.Default..0.0.0..AND DOMINICAN GIRLS\NGOT THAT FLAVOR
Dialogue: 0.0:10:32.73.0:10:34.10.Default..0.0.0..THAT AN ITALIAN GUY NEEDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:34.13.0:10:36.54.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA HAVE. LIKE.\NTEN OF YOUR BABIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:36.56.0:10:38.11.Default..0.0.0..TEN?\NLIKE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:38.13.0:10:39.38.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. TEN OF THEM?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:39.40.0:10:41.21.Default..0.0.0..SO TONIGHT.\NWE'RE GONNA HAVE TEN BABIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:41.24.0:10:43.15.Default..0.0.0..I WAS... I WAS SERIOUS.\NTHOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:43.17.0:10:44.75.Default..0.0.0..I'M DEAD-ASS SERIOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:44.77.0:10:46.15.Default..0.0.0..AS SOON AS I SEE A GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:46.17.0:10:47.69.Default..0.0.0..I ALWAYS LOOK\NTO THE RIGHT OR LEFT OF HER
Dialogue: 0.0:10:47.71.0:10:50.32.Default..0.0.0..TO SEE IF THE GIRL\NHAS A CUTE FRIEND
Dialogue: 0.0:10:50.35.0:10:51.49.Default..0.0.0..FOR MY BOY PAULY.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.51.0:10:53.56.Default..0.0.0..YO. WOULD YOU BE THE GODFATHER\NOF MY BABY TOO?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.58.0:10:55.26.Default..0.0.0..OH. HELL. YEAH.\NHELL. YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.28.0:10:57.33.Default..0.0.0..ME AND VINNY GOT A SET OF CHICKS\NTHAT ARE D.T.F.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.35.0:11:00.00.Default..0.0.0..AND WE ARE TAKING THEM HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.02.0:11:01.62.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO OUT THAT WAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.29.0:11:05.04.Default..0.0.0..YO. YOU FOLLOWING ME. BRO?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:05.06.0:11:06.10.Default..0.0.0..YO. YOU LOOKING\NAT MY GIRL. BRO?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.13.0:11:07.99.Default..0.0.0..YOU FOLLOWING ME. BRO?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.10.0:11:13.58.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO.\NSTAY OR GO?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.60.0:11:14.65.Default..0.0.0..WE NEED TO KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.67.0:11:16.28.Default..0.0.0..WANNA LEAVE?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:16.30.0:11:18.75.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU THINK VINNY\NBROUGHT SOMEBODY HOME?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.77.0:11:20.22.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.24.0:11:22.79.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I WANNA TOUCH VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:22.81.0:11:26.66.Default..0.0.0..JUST DON'T BLOW\NYOUR FRIENDSHIP. YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.68.0:11:29.03.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA TOUCH VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.05.0:11:31.06.Default..0.0.0..THAT POOR GIRL SNOOKI.\NSHE PRETTY MUCH IS LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:31.09.0:11:32.46.Default..0.0.0.."I WANNA GO HOME TO VINNY."
Dialogue: 0.0:11:32.49.0:11:34.85.Default..0.0.0..I WAS LIKE. "ALL RIGHT.\NLET'S GO HOME TO VINNY."
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.06.0:11:44.04.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T TAKE LAURA\NTO THE SMUSH ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:44.07.0:11:45.61.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I GOT A BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:45.63.0:11:49.08.Default..0.0.0..PAULY KNOWS HOW TO NOT\NCOCK BLOCK ME IN THE ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.10.0:11:51.15.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW HOW TO NOT COCK BLOCK\NPAULY IN THE ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:51.17.0:11:53.47.Default..0.0.0..IT'S KIND OF LIKE WE HAVE\NOUR OWN INDIVIDUAL SMUSH ROOMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.25.0:12:01.58.Default..0.0.0..WHERE'S VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:04.39.0:12:05.75.Default..0.0.0..VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.06.0:12:10.97.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:10.99.0:12:12.57.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S STRAIGHT UP\NCRYING OVER YOU
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.59.0:12:14.34.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI'S BEING A HYPOCRITE\NFOR BEING MAD AT ME
Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.36.0:12:15.57.Default..0.0.0..FOR HAVING A GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:15.60.0:12:17.78.Default..0.0.0..MEANWHILE. SNOOKI HOOKS UP\NWITH ALL OF SEASIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:17.80.0:12:19.01.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA BE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:19.03.0:12:20.31.Default..0.0.0..YOU DIDN'T BRING HOME A GUY\NTWO NIGHTS AGO?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:21.34.0:12:23.01.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. YOU'RE SCARING ME!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:23.04.0:12:24.52.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:32.41.0:12:33.39.Default..0.0.0..♪ OOH ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:12:35.88.0:12:38.50.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FUN.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:38.52.0:12:39.52.Default..0.0.0..WHERE'S VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.36.0:12:44.34.Default..0.0.0..WHO'S IN THERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:44.36.0:12:47.27.Default..0.0.0..EWW.\NDOES VINNY HAS A GIRL?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:47.30.0:12:48.97.Default..0.0.0..WHO DO YOU HAVE?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:49.00.0:12:52.41.Default..0.0.0..HEY. HEY.\NHEY. HEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:52.43.0:12:54.28.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}UNO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:54.30.0:12:56.05.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}DOS. DOS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.07.0:12:58.72.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}DOS. UNO. DOS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:58.74.0:13:00.65.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}UNO. DOS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.68.0:13:01.77.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}TRES.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.58.0:13:06.49.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S NOT OKAY. RONALD.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:06.51.0:13:07.93.Default..0.0.0..MAN. GET OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:09.52.0:13:11.13.Default..0.0.0..I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:11.15.0:13:12.76.Default..0.0.0..I HATE YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:12.79.0:13:14.03.Default..0.0.0..I HATE YOU. RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:14.06.0:13:15.43.Default..0.0.0..I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.46.0:13:16.53.Default..0.0.0..WHAT ARE YOU DOING TO HER?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:16.56.0:13:17.67.Default..0.0.0..RON. I NEED TO GO PEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.69.0:13:18.77.Default..0.0.0..NO. THAT'S NOT OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:18.79.0:13:19.77.Default..0.0.0..RON. LET ME GO PISS.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:19.80.0:13:21.17.Default..0.0.0..GO PISS UPSTAIRS.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:21.20.0:13:22.17.Default..0.0.0..GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.20.0:13:24.24.Default..0.0.0..WHERE ARE WE GOING?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:24.27.0:13:25.48.Default..0.0.0..HE LIKES YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:25.50.0:13:27.34.Default..0.0.0..GET IT THROUGH YOUR HEAD.\NOKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.37.0:13:29.91.Default..0.0.0..SO I CAN'T GO TO HIS ROOM\NRIGHT NOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:29.94.0:13:31.08.Default..0.0.0..NO. BECAUSE YOU KNOW WHAT\NTHAT'S GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:31.11.0:13:32.32.Default..0.0.0..IT'S GONNA 'CAUSE\NA BIG FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:32.34.0:13:33.72.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S A GIRL\NAND THERE'S A BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:33.74.0:13:36.65.Default..0.0.0..VINNY BROUGHT A GIRL HOME?\NSHH.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:36.68.0:13:39.39.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T NEED ANYBODY\NTO MAKE YOU FEEL THAT WAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:39.41.0:13:40.99.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE HOT.\NYOU CAN GET WHOEVER YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:41.02.0:13:43.13.Default..0.0.0..SAM'S. LIKE. GOING ALONG.\NLIKE A LITTLE FUCKIN' PUPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.15.0:13:44.36.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE. YOU DON'T DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:44.39.0:13:45.40.Default..0.0.0..THEY'RE GETTING IT IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.42.0:13:46.40.Default..0.0.0..YOU SEE THE LIGHT'S OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:46.42.0:13:47.67.Default..0.0.0..LEAVE 'EM ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:47.69.0:13:49.57.Default..0.0.0..VINNY BROUGHT\NA FUCKIN' GIRL HOME!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:51.16.0:13:52.30.Default..0.0.0..SNOOK. SNOOK.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.33.0:13:53.70.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.\NREALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:53.73.0:13:55.77.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. WE'RE BETTER OFF\NWITHOUT ANY GUYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:55.80.0:13:57.28.Default..0.0.0..I'M TELLING YOU.\NSAM. WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:57.30.0:13:59.64.Default..0.0.0..THEY ALWAYS TREAT US\NSO BAD. WHY?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:59.67.0:14:01.41.Default..0.0.0..GUYS ARE FUCKS.\NAND RON IS A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:01.44.0:14:04.31.Default..0.0.0..SO IF I'M GONNA SAY GUYS ARE\NFUCKS AND RON'S IN THE ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:04.34.0:14:05.35.Default..0.0.0..I'M GONNA LOOK\NRIGHT AT HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:05.37.0:14:06.38.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE HE NEEDS TO KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:06.41.0:14:07.38.Default..0.0.0..RON'S NO DIFFERENT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.41.0:14:08.95.Default..0.0.0..HE DOES THE SAME THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.98.0:14:11.42.Default..0.0.0..BIG BROTHER. LITTLE SISTER.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:11.45.0:14:15.59.Default..0.0.0..WERE YOU NOT IN THE BED WITH\NFUCKING GIANNI THE OTHER NIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:15.62.0:14:16.83.Default..0.0.0..COME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:16.85.0:14:18.30.Default..0.0.0..VINNY'S AN ASSHOLE.\NAND THAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:18.32.0:14:20.50.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHY\NRONNIE WOULD GIVE ME ADVICE
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.52.0:14:22.00.Default..0.0.0..WHEN HE'S. LIKE.\NSUCH. LIKE
Dialogue: 0.0:14:22.02.0:14:23.47.Default..0.0.0..A TERRIBLE BOYFRIEND\NWITH SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.49.0:14:24.84.Default..0.0.0..LOOK. LOOK... LOOK...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:24.86.0:14:26.30.Default..0.0.0..GET OFF ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.33.0:14:27.81.Default..0.0.0..GET OFF ME.\NWILL YOU LISTEN TO ME. PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:27.83.0:14:28.84.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING TO BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:28.86.0:14:31.18.Default..0.0.0..AND GOOD NIGHT.\NAND GOOD NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:31.20.0:14:33.95.Default..0.0.0..SO FUCKING OVER VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:33.97.0:14:35.45.Default..0.0.0..I'M LOOKING OUT\NFOR THE BOTH OF THEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.47.0:14:37.74.Default..0.0.0..DON'T ACT LIKE A DRUNK FUCK.\NTHOUGH. RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:41.94.0:14:43.39.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:43.41.0:14:44.86.Default..0.0.0..BUT IT'S NOT\NOUR TIME RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:44.88.0:14:47.86.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE IN THE FUTURE. YOU KNOW.\NIF HE GROWS UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:47.88.0:14:49.86.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW. I DON'T THINK\NHE'S REALLY GETTING IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.89.0:14:51.43.Default..0.0.0..LIKE WHERE I'M COMING FROM.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:51.45.0:14:53.16.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T BE IN A RELATIONSHIP\NWITH SOMEBODY
Dialogue: 0.0:14:53.19.0:14:54.53.Default..0.0.0..LIKE A CHEATER AND A LIAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:54.56.0:14:56.80.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:56.83.0:14:58.47.Default..0.0.0..WAIT. I'M SO FUCKED\NRIGHT NOW. BECAUSE...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:58.49.0:15:02.17.Default..0.0.0..LOOK AT ME.\NNO. LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:02.20.0:15:03.21.Default..0.0.0..I'M DONE...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.23.0:15:05.44.Default..0.0.0..FALLING FOR THE BULLSHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:05.47.0:15:07.38.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA JUST\NFALL BACK INTO YOUR ARMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:07.40.0:15:09.28.Default..0.0.0..I'M GETTING MIND-FUCKED\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:09.30.0:15:10.85.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. THEN. I'M GONNA GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.87.0:15:13.02.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I DON'T WANT\NTO DO THAT TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:13.04.0:15:14.82.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON\NIN SAM'S HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.84.0:15:16.49.Default..0.0.0..EVERY TIME SHE SAYS.\N"I'M DONE. I'M DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:16.51.0:15:18.06.Default..0.0.0.."WE'RE DONE. I'M DONE.\NYOU'RE DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:18.08.0:15:19.29.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE DONE. I'M DONE.\NYOU'RE DONE."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:19.31.0:15:21.06.Default..0.0.0..♪ DA DA DA DA\NDONE DONE DONE DONE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:15:21.08.0:15:22.99.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I DON'T EVEN KNOW\NAT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.02.0:15:24.80.Default..0.0.0..REALLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:24.82.0:15:26.06.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE IT'S NOT OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:26.09.0:15:27.53.Default..0.0.0..IT'S NOT OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:27.56.0:15:29.22.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS RIDICULOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:31.43.0:15:33.14.Default..0.0.0..JERSEY TURNPIKE THAT SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.16.0:15:35.24.Default..0.0.0..ME AND DEENA DECIDED\NTO WALK HOME FROM THE CLUB.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.26.0:15:36.44.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE HELL\NWE'RE DOING.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:36.46.0:15:38.54.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO PEE.\NCAN I PEE?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.57.0:15:39.94.Default..0.0.0..I'M GONNA PEE\NRIGHT OVER HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.97.0:15:41.85.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE A NAPKIN\NIN MY PURSE!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.87.0:15:44.05.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE A NAPKIN\NWITH A NUMBER.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:44.07.0:15:46.28.Default..0.0.0..IT'S A NAPKIN.\NBUT IT'S A NUMBER ON IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:46.31.0:15:47.55.Default..0.0.0..I'LL KEEP IT ALWAYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:47.58.0:15:49.85.Default..0.0.0..EWW! YOU PEED ON MY FOOT!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:49.88.0:15:51.62.Default..0.0.0..EWW! EWW!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:51.65.0:15:53.42.Default..0.0.0..I GOT PEE ON MY FOOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:53.45.0:15:55.13.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG\NWITH ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:55.15.0:15:56.96.Default..0.0.0..YOU PEED ON MY FOOT.\NI WANT YOU TO WIPE IT OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.99.0:15:58.51.Default..0.0.0..I'LL WIPE IT OFF\NIN THE HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:59.69.0:16:00.83.Default..0.0.0..HOW YOU DOIN'?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:00.86.0:16:04.04.Default..0.0.0..UM. COULD I ALSO HAVE\NANOTHER CAB. PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:04.06.0:16:05.37.Default..0.0.0..WANNA CUDDLE ME TONIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.39.0:16:06.59.Default..0.0.0..I WILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:08.96.0:16:10.03.Default..0.0.0..WOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:11.87.0:16:13.58.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T HOLD MY PEE ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.60.0:16:15.18.Default..0.0.0..WHO IS THESE GIRLS?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:15.20.0:16:16.52.Default..0.0.0..COME IN HERE.\NCOME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:19.01.0:16:21.35.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE VINNY'S NOT\NTHE ONE FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:21.38.0:16:23.42.Default..0.0.0..BUT SOMEBODY OUT THERE IS.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.45.0:16:25.56.Default..0.0.0..I'LL CUDDLE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:25.58.0:16:28.36.Default..0.0.0..HE BROUGHT SOMEBODY HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:28.38.0:16:30.83.Default..0.0.0..COME ON. SHE LOOKED LIKE\NA FUCKING RODENT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.19.0:16:35.73.Default..0.0.0..HIT ME UP.\NALL RIGHT. I WILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:35.76.0:16:37.03.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS... IT WAS NICE\NTO MEET YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.06.0:16:38.64.Default..0.0.0..BYE. VINNY.\NBYE-BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:38.66.0:16:40.40.Default..0.0.0..COME ON. YOU KNOW\NHE'S DOING IT ON PURPOSE
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.43.0:16:41.40.Default..0.0.0..TO GET A RISE\NOUT OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:41.43.0:16:42.87.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.90.0:16:44.41.Default..0.0.0..HE'S SUCH A PIG.\NJUST LIKE RON IS.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:44.43.0:16:46.08.Default..0.0.0..HE'S SUCH A PIG.\NI'M SO OVER IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.10.0:16:48.25.Default..0.0.0..YO. SHE'S LIKE CRYING\NRIGHT NOW OVER YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:48.27.0:16:49.81.Default..0.0.0..JUST SO YOU KNOW.\NTHAT'S SO STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.84.0:16:51.25.Default..0.0.0..SHE WASN'T CRYING\NTHE OTHER NIGHT WITH GIANNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.27.0:16:53.58.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT I SAID TO HER.\NBUT THAT'S HER DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:53.61.0:16:55.79.Default..0.0.0..SHE GETS WITH GIR-\NGUYS EVERY TIME SHE CAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:55.81.0:16:57.25.Default..0.0.0..SHE WANTS TO HAVE SEX WITH ME.\NMEANWHILE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.28.0:16:58.39.Default..0.0.0..SHE GETS WITH A KID\NTHE NIGHT BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:58.41.0:17:00.83.Default..0.0.0..GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:00.85.0:17:02.16.Default..0.0.0..CAN YOU GO IN THERE\NAND TALK TO HER?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:02.18.0:17:03.63.Default..0.0.0..JENNI. COME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.65.0:17:05.26.Default..0.0.0..I'M... WHAT DID I DO WRONG?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:05.29.0:17:06.63.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NBUT SHE'S STRAIGHT UP
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.65.0:17:08.27.Default..0.0.0..CRYING OVER YOU RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:08.29.0:17:10.13.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI'S BEING A HYPOCRITE\NFOR BEING MAD AT ME
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.16.0:17:11.84.Default..0.0.0..FOR HAVING A GIRL.\NMEANWHILE. SNOOKI
Dialogue: 0.0:17:11.86.0:17:13.24.Default..0.0.0..HOOKS UP\NWITH ALL OF SEASIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.30.0:17:16.51.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.53.0:17:18.08.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. WHY ARE YOU CRYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:18.10.0:17:19.94.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WHY ARE YOU CRYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:19.97.0:17:21.85.Default..0.0.0..TELL ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:21.87.0:17:24.52.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA BE WITH YOU.\NYOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:24.54.0:17:26.38.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. YOU DIDN'T BRING HOME\NA GUY TWO NIGHTS AGO?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:26.41.0:17:27.68.Default..0.0.0..VINNY. STOP.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.71.0:17:28.82.Default..0.0.0..YOU DIDN'T BRING HOME A GUY\NTWO NIGHTS AGO?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:28.84.0:17:30.65.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:30.68.0:17:33.19.Default..0.0.0..JUST GO HAVE\NFUCKING FUN.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.21.0:17:34.33.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. YOU'RE DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:34.35.0:17:36.06.Default..0.0.0..TOMORROW. WE'RE GONNA\NTALK ABOUT THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.08.0:17:37.40.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'S GONNA BE ALL GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.42.0:17:38.40.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T CARE IF YOU'RE MAD\NAT ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:38.42.0:17:39.89.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANT YOU TO BE OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.99.0:17:44.34.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.36.0:17:45.77.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NI GUESS I'M WRONG.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.79.0:17:47.80.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I CAN HANDLE HER\NGETTING WITH GUYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:47.83.0:17:51.24.Default..0.0.0..AND SHE'S UPSET THAT I HAD\NA GIRL HOME TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:51.27.0:17:54.08.Default..0.0.0..SO IF I'M A PIECE OF SHIT.\NI'M A PIECE OF SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.17.0:18:02.59.Default..0.0.0..SHE IS STARTING TO GROW\NSOME FEELINGS FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.61.0:18:04.56.Default..0.0.0..DO THE RIGHT THING.\NVINCENZO.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:04.58.0:18:06.39.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN HE'S BRINGING HOME\NALL THESE GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.41.0:18:08.26.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU FULLY GAY?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:08.28.0:18:09.59.Default..0.0.0..AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.62.0:18:11.53.Default..0.0.0..FUCK MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.55.0:18:12.96.Default..0.0.0..NASTY. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.99.0:18:14.40.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'D YOU DO\NTO OUR BATHROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.42.0:18:15.70.Default..0.0.0..ME?\NTHAT'S DISGUSTING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.72.0:18:17.44.Default..0.0.0..NOBODY IN THIS HOUSE\NOWNS UP TO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.46.0:18:18.60.Default..0.0.0..CLEAN THAT BATHROOM.\NI'M NOT TOUCHING IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.63.0:18:19.70.Default..0.0.0..VINNY...
Dialogue: 0.0:18:19.73.0:18:20.70.Default..0.0.0..FUCKIN' STINKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.54.0:18:35.05.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS WANNA DO BOWLING?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.08.0:18:37.19.Default..0.0.0..NICOLEY. GET YOUR BUTT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.21.0:18:38.46.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GOING BOWLING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:38.48.0:18:41.63.Default..0.0.0..GET YOUR LITTLE\NGUIDO BUTT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:41.65.0:18:43.03.Default..0.0.0..I'M A LITTLE DEPRESSED\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.05.0:18:44.23.Default..0.0.0..JUST BECAUSE EVERYONE'S\NGOING BOWLING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.25.0:18:45.76.Default..0.0.0..THEY'RE GOING OUT TO EAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:45.79.0:18:48.17.Default..0.0.0..AND I JUST CAN'T GET OUT OF BED\N'CAUSE I'M SO TIRED.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:48.19.0:18:49.20.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO HUNG OVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:49.22.0:18:51.10.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M STILL MAD AT VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:52.73.0:18:54.07.Default..0.0.0..YO!\NLET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.10.0:18:55.11.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE LEAVING!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.13.0:18:56.97.Default..0.0.0..MIKE! LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.00.0:18:58.88.Default..0.0.0..WHO'S DRIVING?\NI'M DRIVING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:58.90.0:19:00.58.Default..0.0.0..I'M ACTUALLY A GOOD DRIVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.60.0:19:03.48.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI'S NOT COMING. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.50.0:19:04.58.Default..0.0.0..I'LL FOLLOW THEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:04.61.0:19:06.48.Default..0.0.0..DOES EVERYBODY\NHAVE THEIR SEATBELTS ON?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:06.51.0:19:08.25.Default..0.0.0..I MISS DRIVING.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:08.28.0:19:11.29.Default..0.0.0..WOW. DEENA JUST MADE\NTHE MOST AWFUL TURN
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.31.0:19:13.29.Default..0.0.0..I'VE EVER SEEN IN MY LIFE.\NDEENA'S DRIVING?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:13.31.0:19:14.76.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE HELL?\NTHAT WAS BAD?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:14.78.0:19:16.39.Default..0.0.0..GIRL IS OUT OF CONTROL.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.42.0:19:18.43.Default..0.0.0..I JUST SPILLED MY COFFEE.\NAND I DON'T EVEN DRINK COFFEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:18.45.0:19:21.03.Default..0.0.0..SHE TURNED AND ALMOST WENT\NINTO THE CARS ON THIS SIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.06.0:19:22.23.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. MOVE TO THE LEFT.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:22.26.0:19:23.40.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.\NI'M FINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:23.42.0:19:24.80.Default..0.0.0..MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:24.83.0:19:26.60.Default..0.0.0..LITERALLY. WE'RE ON THE PARKWAY\NON THE WAY TO BOWLING.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:26.63.0:19:28.44.Default..0.0.0..AND OUR CAR WAS GOING\NOFF THE LANE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:28.46.0:19:29.84.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. INTO THE SIDE RAILING.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:30.97.0:19:32.98.Default..0.0.0..DEENA. YOU'RE SCARING ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.00.0:19:34.55.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:34.57.0:19:37.31.Default..0.0.0..DEENA MIGHT BE THE WORST\NDRIVER IN THE TRISTATE AREA.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:37.34.0:19:38.95.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. I WAS SCARED\NFOR MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.94.0:19:43.95.Default..0.0.0..WHAT WAS THAT?\NCOME ON!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.98.0:19:45.76.Default..0.0.0..WHAT WAS IT?\NWE'RE GONNA FUCKIN' DIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.78.0:19:48.23.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS THE WORST DECISION\NFOR HER TO EVER DRIVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.25.0:19:49.39.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.\NWAIT CHECK IN HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:49.42.0:19:50.76.Default..0.0.0..I MIGHT HAVE A NAPKIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:50.79.0:19:51.79.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.25.0:19:54.53.Default..0.0.0..I KEPT SAYING.\N"WE'RE GONNA DIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.56.0:19:55.67.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DIE.\NWE'RE GONNA DIE."
Dialogue: 0.0:19:57.53.0:19:59.50.Default..0.0.0..AH. YOU'RE GETTIN' DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.53.0:20:00.50.Default..0.0.0..YOU GOT BLUE BALLS?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.53.0:20:01.76.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:04.13.0:20:06.98.Default..0.0.0..YOU ARE NOT DRIVING HOME.\NLITTLE BLAST.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:07.00.0:20:09.11.Default..0.0.0..OHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:09.14.0:20:11.65.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA KISS THE GROUND\NI'M NOT DEAD RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.67.0:20:13.67.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?\NIT WAS THAT BAD?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:18.15.0:20:19.15.Default..0.0.0..DAMN!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.88.0:20:22.26.Default..0.0.0..BOWL FOR HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:22.28.0:20:23.46.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.48.0:20:24.46.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.49.0:20:26.13.Default..0.0.0..WITH MY GIRL.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.15.0:20:27.60.Default..0.0.0..IT'S MORE COMPLICATED\NTHAN THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.62.0:20:28.77.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DO YOU\NLIKE HER OR NO?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:28.79.0:20:30.23.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.26.0:20:33.40.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S STARTING TO GROW\NSOME FEELINGS FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:33.43.0:20:36.27.Default..0.0.0..STAY! BREAK!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.30.0:20:37.37.Default..0.0.0..STEE-RIKE!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:37.40.0:20:38.58.Default..0.0.0..NO. SHE'S LIKE\NCRYING HYSTERICALLY
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.60.0:20:39.81.Default..0.0.0..ALL DAY AND NIGHT OVER YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:39.83.0:20:41.91.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW. I DON'T\NWANT HER TO CRY. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.94.0:20:43.38.Default..0.0.0..I THINK YOU GUYS\NSHOULD HAVE YOUR OWN TALK.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.40.0:20:45.95.Default..0.0.0..NONE OF MY BUSINESS.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.97.0:20:48.18.Default..0.0.0..SHE JUST CREEPS UP ON ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:48.21.0:20:49.92.Default..0.0.0..LIKE ALL OF A SUDDEN.\NEVERYTHING'S FINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.94.0:20:51.45.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S HOOKIN' UP WITH GUYS.\NYOU DO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:51.48.0:20:53.48.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN.\NSHE STARTS CRYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.22.0:20:59.12.Default..0.0.0..DO THE RIGHT THING.\NVINCENZO.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:01.89.0:21:04.10.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T FEEL LIKE BOWLING\NANYMORE; I'M DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:04.12.0:21:05.64.Default..0.0.0..HAVE YOUR SHOES\NAND EVERYTHING?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:08.50.0:21:10.70.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T MAKE LEFTS\NIN FUCKIN' JERSEY. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:16.17.0:21:18.22.Default..0.0.0..YOU ALL RIGHT?\NYOU BETTER?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:18.24.0:21:20.15.Default..0.0.0..FEEL EMBARRASSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:20.17.0:21:22.09.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REMEMBER\NLEAVING THE CLUB.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:22.11.0:21:23.92.Default..0.0.0..THE WHOLE TIME.\NYOU WERE TALKING ABOUT
Dialogue: 0.0:21:23.94.0:21:26.49.Default..0.0.0..HOW MUCH YOU LIKE VINNY\NAND LOVE VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:26.51.0:21:28.99.Default..0.0.0..I JUST REMEMBER HEARING YOU\NCRYING THE WHOLE NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:29.02.0:21:31.33.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU HAVE FEELINGS FOR HIM.\NOR YOU WERE DRUNK?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:31.35.0:21:33.00.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. I LIKE HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:33.02.0:21:35.07.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. YOU{\i1} LIKE{\i0} LIKE HIM?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:35.09.0:21:37.33.Default..0.0.0..I THINK SO.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.36.0:21:38.50.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S NOT GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:38.53.0:21:41.00.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE THEN WHY\NWOULD I SAY THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.03.0:21:42.74.Default..0.0.0..I-I THINK I LIKE HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:42.76.0:21:44.58.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. HE'S A COMFORT ZONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.60.0:21:46.54.Default..0.0.0..HE'S ALWAYS THE ONE\NTHAT YOU CAN FALL BACK ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:46.57.0:21:48.17.Default..0.0.0..AND HE'S YOUR ROOMMATE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.37.0:21:54.45.Default..0.0.0..I THOUGHT YOU WERE JUST DRUNK\NAND BEING STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:54.48.0:21:55.72.Default..0.0.0..I WAS LIKE.\N"SHE'S GONNA WAKE UP TOMORROW
Dialogue: 0.0:21:55.74.0:21:56.95.Default..0.0.0..AND NOT EVEN KNOW WHAT\NTHE FUCK SHE DID."
Dialogue: 0.0:21:56.98.0:21:57.96.Default..0.0.0..I'M EMBARRASSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:57.98.0:22:00.02.Default..0.0.0..FUCK MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:00.05.0:22:02.56.Default..0.0.0..IT'S JUST NOT A GOOD LOOK\NFOR ME TO. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:02.58.0:22:04.56.Default..0.0.0..STARTING TO HAVE. LIKE.\NFEELINGS FOR HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.59.0:22:06.03.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. LIKING HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:06.05.0:22:07.67.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN HE'S BRINGING HOME\NALL THESE GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:07.69.0:22:09.57.Default..0.0.0..TELLING ME HE'S NOT\NGONNA BRING ANYONE HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:09.59.0:22:11.94.Default..0.0.0..SO WE CAN CUDDLE. AND THEN\NHE BRINGS SOMEBODY HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:11.96.0:22:13.48.Default..0.0.0..IT JUST MAKES ME\NLOOK STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:16.53.0:22:18.58.Default..0.0.0..IS SHE EMBARRASSED?\NI THINK...
Dialogue: 0.0:22:18.60.0:22:20.21.Default..0.0.0..I THINK SHE'S EMBARRASSED.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:20.23.0:22:22.11.Default..0.0.0..I THINK. JUST. EVERYTHING\NTHAT'S BEEN GOING ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:22.14.0:22:23.41.Default..0.0.0..THE WHOLE NICK THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:23.44.0:22:24.92.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE ONE THING\NAFTER ANOTHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:24.94.0:22:26.68.Default..0.0.0..I THINK SHE JUST\NLOOKS FOR RELATIONSHIPS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:26.71.0:22:28.25.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT IT IS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:28.28.0:22:30.02.Default..0.0.0..AND I THINK EVERY GUY SHE DOES\NSTART TO TALK TO.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:30.04.0:22:31.39.Default..0.0.0..SHE THINKS OF IT AS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:31.41.0:22:33.26.Default..0.0.0.."THIS COULD BE MY BOYFRIEND."\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:33.28.0:22:34.36.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S NOT THE TYPE OF GIRL
Dialogue: 0.0:22:34.38.0:22:35.93.Default..0.0.0..THAT CAN JUST HOOK UP\NWITH SOMEBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:35.95.0:22:37.33.Default..0.0.0..THAT SUCKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:37.35.0:22:38.40.Default..0.0.0..IT DOES SUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:38.42.0:22:40.96.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL BAD.\NI KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:40.99.0:22:46.94.Default..0.0.0..♪ LEAVE ME ALONE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:46.96.0:22:49.47.Default..0.0.0..YOU OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:49.50.0:22:50.47.Default..0.0.0..CAN I STAY HERE FOR A SECOND?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:50.50.0:22:52.78.Default..0.0.0..NO! MM-MMM.\NNO?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:52.80.0:22:54.65.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANT TO BE ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:54.67.0:22:57.31.Default..0.0.0..GO AWAY.\NGO AWAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:57.34.0:23:02.85.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'M TRYING\NTO GET AWAY NOW ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.88.0:23:05.92.Default..0.0.0..♪ AND THEN I LOST MY MIND ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:23:05.95.0:23:08.53.Default..0.0.0..♪ I LOST MY MIND ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.55.0:23:14.00.Default..0.0.0..♪ BUT IT ALWAYS\NFINDS ME AGAIN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:23:14.02.0:23:15.75.Default..0.0.0..♪ I'M TRYING TO GET AWAY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:23:19.33.0:23:21.74.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.76.0:23:23.41.Default..0.0.0..THAT FAT ONE IS ACTUALLY\NKIND OF CUTE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.43.0:23:25.11.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I WOULD DEFINITELY.\NLIKE. HANG OUT WITH THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:25.13.0:23:26.41.Default..0.0.0..NICE MUSCLES.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.43.0:23:27.58.Default..0.0.0..S.T.D. FROM WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:27.60.0:23:28.75.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN'T GET\NAN S.T.D. FROM THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.77.0:23:30.25.Default..0.0.0..WOULD YOU LIKE TO CALL\NTHAT DOCTOR IN THERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:30.27.0:23:32.02.Default..0.0.0..IT WON'T BE LONG BEFORE\NMIKE'S DICK FALLS OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:32.04.0:23:33.10.Default..0.0.0..OHH!\NOHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.95.0:23:45.70.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS LIKE\NTHE PERFECT SUNDAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:45.72.0:23:47.20.Default..0.0.0..YO. THAT BATHROOM'S\NGROSS AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:47.22.0:23:49.40.Default..0.0.0..I JUST CLEANED IT\NTWO DAYS AGO.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:49.42.0:23:51.07.Default..0.0.0..I WAS GONNA TOUCH IT.\NAND I'M NOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:51.09.0:23:52.54.Default..0.0.0..I CLEANED THAT-\NI CAN'T CLEAN IT AGAIN FOR THE...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:52.56.0:23:54.47.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT DOING IT-\NI'LL LET BUGS GO IN THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:54.49.0:23:56.01.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'D YOU DO\NTO OUR BATHROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:56.03.0:23:57.07.Default..0.0.0..ME?\NIT'S DISGUSTING.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:57.10.0:23:58.71.Default..0.0.0..ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:58.73.0:24:00.11.Default..0.0.0..NOBODY IN THIS HOUSE\NOWNS UP TO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:00.13.0:24:01.48.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S A CLOGGED TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:01.50.0:24:03.15.Default..0.0.0..NOBODY KNOWS WHO DID IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:03.17.0:24:05.08.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S LIKE A FUCKIN' GHOST\NIN THIS HOUSE OR SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:05.11.0:24:07.89.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING INTO YOUR NASTY-ASS\NFUCKIN' BATHROOM. SO...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:07.91.0:24:08.89.Default..0.0.0..WAIT TILL HE\NOPENS THAT TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:08.91.0:24:09.92.Default..0.0.0..HE'S GONNA TURN RIGHT AROUND.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:09.94.0:24:11.09.Default..0.0.0..NO. HE...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:11.11.0:24:14.43.Default..0.0.0..IT IS... IT IS BEYOND\NSTINKY IN THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:14.45.0:24:15.71.Default..0.0.0..IT'S SO GROSS.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:26.49.0:24:28.29.Default..0.0.0..LET ME IN. MOFO.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:30.00.0:24:32.74.Default..0.0.0..All: OHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:34.44.0:24:35.78.Default..0.0.0..WHAT IS THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:35.80.0:24:37.31.Default..0.0.0..OH. DID SOMEBODY\NJUST SHIT IN IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:37.34.0:24:38.72.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:38.74.0:24:40.55.Default..0.0.0..I THINK SOMEBODY\NSTILL SHIT IN IT!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:40.57.0:24:41.99.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.01.0:24:44.05.Default..0.0.0..I'M CHOKING ON THE SMELL.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:44.08.0:24:45.72.Default..0.0.0..I CAN TASTE IT\NIN MY MOUTH RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:48.42.0:24:49.73.Default..0.0.0..LET ME SEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:49.75.0:24:51.09.Default..0.0.0..OHH! OHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:51.12.0:24:52.83.Default..0.0.0..OH. THERE GOES-\NTHAT WATER'S GREEN. BRO!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:52.85.0:24:54.23.Default..0.0.0..WATER'S GREEN!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:54.26.0:24:55.83.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW. IT'S LIKE ALGAE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:55.86.0:24:59.07.Default..0.0.0..OHH!\NOHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:59.09.0:25:01.17.Default..0.0.0..AH. THAT FUCKIN' STINKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:02.93.0:25:04.21.Default..0.0.0..AAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:04.23.0:25:06.88.Default..0.0.0..THE SMELL IS JUST\N"PERMINATING" THROUGH THE AIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:06.90.0:25:08.75.Default..0.0.0..IT IS JUST...
Dialogue: 0.0:25:08.77.0:25:10.48.Default..0.0.0..IT'S JUST NOT A GOOD\NSITUATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:10.50.0:25:11.95.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T EVEN ELABORATE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:11.97.0:25:12.98.Default..0.0.0..WHO TOOK ANOTHER\NSHIT IN THERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:13.01.0:25:13.98.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE THAT. IT WAS LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:25:14.01.0:25:15.02.Default..0.0.0..NOBODY COULD DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:15.04.0:25:16.19.Default..0.0.0..SOMEBODY DID IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:16.21.0:25:17.96.Default..0.0.0..SOMEBODY TOOK AN EXTRA\NSHIT IN IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:17.98.0:25:19.96.Default..0.0.0..WHY DO THEY DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.98.0:25:22.56.Default..0.0.0..IF THERE'S A PLUMBER\NIN THIS UNIVERSE
Dialogue: 0.0:25:22.58.0:25:25.00.Default..0.0.0..THAT WILL FACE THE SHIT\NIN MY TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:25.02.0:25:26.96.Default..0.0.0..HE DESERVES A MEDAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:26.99.0:25:29.07.Default..0.0.0..HELP!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:31.29.0:25:32.64.Default..0.0.0..HELLO. SHORE STORE.\NDANNY SPEAKING.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:32.66.0:25:34.27.Default..0.0.0..DANNY. IT'S JENNI.\NHEY. WHAT'S UP. JENNI?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:34.30.0:25:35.44.Default..0.0.0..HOW WE DOING?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:35.46.0:25:37.84.Default..0.0.0..WE HAVE AN EMERGENCY\NWITH THAT TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:37.87.0:25:39.64.Default..0.0.0..I THOUGHT YOU GUYS TOOK CARE\NOF THAT A LONG TIME AGO.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.67.0:25:42.75.Default..0.0.0..NO. IT NEVER GOT FIXED.\NSO WE NEED YOUR HELP.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:42.77.0:25:44.08.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:44.10.0:25:45.78.Default..0.0.0..THAT MAKES TOTAL SENSE TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:45.81.0:25:48.35.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW. WE'RE ASSHOLES.\NI GET IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:48.38.0:25:49.85.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY. I CAN'T\NDO NOTHIN' FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:49.88.0:25:51.19.Default..0.0.0..IT'S SUNDAY NIGHT.\NI'M KIND OF BUSY.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:51.21.0:25:52.49.Default..0.0.0..JUST LIKE EVERY OTHER PLUMBER.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:52.51.0:25:54.83.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS SHOULD HAVE TAKEN CARE\NOF THIS DAYS AGO.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:54.85.0:25:56.49.Default..0.0.0..TOMORROW. I CAN HAVE THAT\NTAKEN CARE OF.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:56.52.0:25:58.50.Default..0.0.0..BUT TONIGHT. YOU GUYS'LL\NJUST HAVE TO DEAL WITH IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:58.52.0:26:00.06.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.\NALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:00.09.0:26:02.93.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. BYE.\NLATER. BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:02.96.0:26:05.62.Default..0.0.0..THIS SUCKS BALL SACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:13.77.0:26:15.61.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE IF SOME OF OUR\NBATHROOMS WERE FIXED.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:15.64.0:26:17.01.Default..0.0.0..SOME OF US COULD USE THEM ALL\NAT THE SAME TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:17.04.0:26:18.55.Default..0.0.0..PLUMBER'S COMING\NAT 11:30.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:24.28.0:26:26.36.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NSMELLS LIKE SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:31.08.0:26:32.60.Default..0.0.0..HELLO. HOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:32.62.0:26:33.70.Default..0.0.0..I'M RICH AND THAT'S MIKE.\NWE'RE THE PLUMBERS.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:33.72.0:26:34.73.Default..0.0.0..OH. HELLO.\NHOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:34.76.0:26:35.90.Default..0.0.0..GOOD. HOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:35.92.0:26:36.97.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S. UH.\NWHAT'S THE PROBLEM?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:36.99.0:26:38.23.Default..0.0.0..YOU MIGHT BE SCARED.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:38.26.0:26:39.24.Default..0.0.0..AH. GREAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:39.26.0:26:41.24.Default..0.0.0..THE PLUMBERS ARE HERE.\NFINALLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:41.26.0:26:43.31.Default..0.0.0..THE FAT ONE IS ACTUALLY\NKIND OF CUTE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:43.33.0:26:44.84.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I WOULD DEFINITELY.\NLIKE. HANG OUT WITH THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:44.87.0:26:46.58.Default..0.0.0..NICE!\NCAN YOU FIX THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:46.60.0:26:49.01.Default..0.0.0..UH... I'M GONNA\NDEFINITELY TRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:49.04.0:26:51.88.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU SCARED?\NNO. I'M NOT SCARED. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:51.91.0:26:53.58.Default..0.0.0..DOES YOUR BUTT CRACK\NHANG OUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:53.61.0:26:55.69.Default..0.0.0..YES. IT DOES. ACTUALLY.\NCOOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:55.71.0:26:57.59.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO GET OUT OF HERE.\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:57.61.0:26:58.69.Default..0.0.0..GOOD LUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:58.71.0:27:00.46.Default..0.0.0..UGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:00.48.0:27:02.66.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. GRAB THE TOILET AUGER\NOFF THE BACK OF THE TRUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:02.68.0:27:04.03.Default..0.0.0..I'LL TRY THAT FIRST.\NAND THEN AFTER THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:04.05.0:27:05.66.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO TAKE\NTHE TOILET OUT. PRETTY MUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:05.69.0:27:06.86.Default..0.0.0..HOW LONG HAS IT\NBEEN LIKE THIS?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:06.89.0:27:08.53.Default..0.0.0..LIKE TWO WEEKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:08.56.0:27:10.60.Default..0.0.0..AH. GOD.\NTHAT'S LOVELY.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:10.62.0:27:12.07.Default..0.0.0..I'M SURPRISED YOU GUYS DON'T\NHAVE MAGGOTS IN HERE YET.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:12.09.0:27:13.40.Default..0.0.0..IT SMELLS SO BAD.\NMAGGOTS?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:13.43.0:27:15.00.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. MAGGOTS. ABSOLUTELY.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:15.03.0:27:16.51.Default..0.0.0..THEY'LL CRAWL\NINTO THE BEDROOMS.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:16.53.0:27:19.34.Default..0.0.0..GET OUT! COME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:19.37.0:27:21.21.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD. I'M GONNA VOMIT.\NEXCUSE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:21.24.0:27:23.60.Default..0.0.0..NICE MUSCLES.\NTHANKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:31.58.0:27:32.92.Default..0.0.0..UGH!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:32.95.0:27:34.32.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T THINK I'M GONNA\NEAT FOR FOUR DAYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:35.58.0:27:36.63.Default..0.0.0..IT'S STUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:36.65.0:27:38.96.Default..0.0.0..SOMEBODY FLUSHED\NA PAIR OF UNDERWEAR...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:38.99.0:27:41.10.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:41.12.0:27:43.53.Default..0.0.0..ACTUALLY. I WOULD HAVE\NTO SAY THAT'S A {bleep} TEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:43.56.0:27:44.90.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S PROBABLY VINNY'S.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.93.0:27:46.30.Default..0.0.0..GIVE IT TO ONE\NOF YOUR HOUSEMATES.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:46.33.0:27:48.84.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. YOU CAN'T FLUSH\N{bleep} TEES DOWN THE TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:48.86.0:27:50.44.Default..0.0.0..NO.\NWHO DOES THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:50.46.0:27:52.34.Default..0.0.0..EWW!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:52.37.0:27:53.48.Default..0.0.0..WORKS NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:53.50.0:27:55.21.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU SCRUB IT CLEAN TOO?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:55.24.0:27:56.88.Default..0.0.0..NO. YOU'RE\NSCRUBBING IT CLEAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:56.90.0:27:58.51.Default..0.0.0..SERIOUSLY?\NSERIOUSLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:58.54.0:27:59.98.Default..0.0.0..I'LL SPRAY IT DOWN\NAS MUCH AS I CAN
Dialogue: 0.0:28:00.01.0:28:02.17.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU HAVE SOME. LIKE.\NCLEANER IN THE HOUSE SOMEWHERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:03.71.0:28:04.89.Default..0.0.0..CASCADE?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:04.91.0:28:06.42.Default..0.0.0..HI. BOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:06.45.0:28:08.09.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:08.11.0:28:09.59.Default..0.0.0..SO GUESS WHY\NTHE TOILET IS CLOGGED.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:09.62.0:28:10.79.Default..0.0.0..WHY?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:10.82.0:28:12.33.Default..0.0.0..SOMEONE FLUSHED\NA FUCKIN' {bleep} TEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:12.35.0:28:14.00.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NSWEAR TO GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:14.02.0:28:16.00.Default..0.0.0..WHO WEARS {bleep} TEES?\NVINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:16.02.0:28:17.00.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA FUCK THEM UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:17.02.0:28:19.10.Default..0.0.0..WATCH THE SPLASH.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:19.13.0:28:21.24.Default..0.0.0..I GUARANTEE IT'S LIKE\NWHEN THEY TOOK A SHOWER.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:21.26.0:28:22.61.Default..0.0.0..THEY FUCKIN' DROPPED IT\NIN THE TOILET
Dialogue: 0.0:28:22.63.0:28:24.07.Default..0.0.0..AND TRIED TO FLUSH IT...\NYOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:24.10.0:28:25.34.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE THEY DIDN'T WANT\NTO PICK IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:25.37.0:28:26.78.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. THEY DIDN'T\NWANT TO PICK IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:26.80.0:28:28.41.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN FLUSH IT A FEW TIMES.\NMAKE SURE THERE'S. LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:28:28.44.0:28:30.31.Default..0.0.0..NOT THE REST OF AN OUTFIT\NDOWN THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:30.34.0:28:32.05.Default..0.0.0..DID WE GET A SIZE\NON THAT {bleep} TEE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.07.0:28:33.08.Default..0.0.0..OR A BRAND?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:33.11.0:28:34.85.Default..0.0.0..OH. YEAH. WHAT SIZE?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:34.88.0:28:35.89.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS A SMALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:35.91.0:28:36.89.Default..0.0.0..SMALL?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.91.0:28:38.69.Default..0.0.0..IT'S VINNY'S!\NVINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:38.71.0:28:40.32.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN USE IT.\NIT'S CLEANED UP A LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:40.35.0:28:41.53.Default..0.0.0..THANKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:41.55.0:28:42.73.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS HAVE A NICE\NREST OF YOUR DAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:42.75.0:28:44.03.Default..0.0.0..AND I'LL SEND THE BOYS\NTHE BILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:44.05.0:28:45.13.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. SEND THE BOYS\NTHE BILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:45.15.0:28:46.53.Default..0.0.0..ABSOLUTELY.\NHAVE A GOOD DAY. GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:46.55.0:28:47.53.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:47.56.0:28:48.83.Default..0.0.0..BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:48.86.0:28:50.66.Default..0.0.0..ALL MY SHIT\NIS GONNA SMELL NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:58.27.0:29:00.94.Default..0.0.0..ROGER. BEEN DYING\NTO TELL YOU THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:00.97.0:29:04.91.Default..0.0.0..SOMEONE FLUSHED A FUCKING\N{bleep} TEE DOWN THE TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:04.94.0:29:07.48.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T WAIT-\NWHOA. WHOA. WHOA! HOLD ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:07.51.0:29:08.62.Default..0.0.0..OH. IT'S THE BIG TIME. YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:08.64.0:29:10.05.Default..0.0.0..WHO'S SHIRT\NWAS IN THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:10.08.0:29:11.69.Default..0.0.0..THAT GRAY ONE.\NBY ANY CHANCE?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:11.71.0:29:12.92.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T SHOWER DOWN THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:12.95.0:29:14.69.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NWHAT'S UP?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:18.59.0:29:21.13.Default..0.0.0..FIND OUT WHO PUT\NTHE {bleep} TEE IN...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:21.15.0:29:22.30.Default..0.0.0..both: THE TOILET?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:22.32.0:29:23.90.Default..0.0.0..VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:25.19.0:29:27.54.Default..0.0.0..WHAT ARE YOU\NLOOKING AT. BRO?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:27.56.0:29:28.54.Default..0.0.0..WHY WOULD I PUT\NA GUINEA TEE
Dialogue: 0.0:29:28.56.0:29:29.57.Default..0.0.0..DOWN MY OWN TOILET?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:29.60.0:29:30.97.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS MY THEORY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:31.00.0:29:33.74.Default..0.0.0..A GUY MIGHT HAVE BEEN\NGETTING IN THE SHOWER OR CHANGE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.77.0:29:35.35.Default..0.0.0..TOOK THE {bleep} TEE OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:35.37.0:29:36.68.Default..0.0.0..IT DROPPED IN THE TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:36.70.0:29:38.62.Default..0.0.0..SOME PEOPLE DON'T WANNA\NPICK SHIT OUT OF THE TOILET.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:38.64.0:29:40.05.Default..0.0.0..SO THEY'RE LIKE. "ALL RIGHT.\NI'M GONNA FLUSH IT."
Dialogue: 0.0:29:40.07.0:29:42.19.Default..0.0.0..THAT IS AN AMAZING\NRATIONALIZATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:42.21.0:29:45.69.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE THERE WAS ANOTHER\NALIEN PLANET OUT IN FRONT.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:45.71.0:29:48.26.Default..0.0.0..AND HE SHOT A LASER BEAM\NTHROUGH THE GLASS
Dialogue: 0.0:29:48.28.0:29:50.06.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU GOT SCARED.\NUSED THE WIFE BEATER
Dialogue: 0.0:29:50.08.0:29:52.00.Default..0.0.0..TO COVER YOUR EYES.\NIT SLIPPED.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:52.02.0:29:53.50.Default..0.0.0..YOU FORGOT THE {bleep} TEE\NWAS OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:53.52.0:29:55.23.Default..0.0.0..YOU DIDN'T WANT\NTHE EVIDENCE OF THE ALIEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:55.26.0:29:57.07.Default..0.0.0..SO YOU PUT IT DOWN THE TOILET\NAND YOU FLUSHED IT AND YOU...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:57.09.0:29:58.30.Default..0.0.0..I GOT IT!\NYOU KNOW WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:58.33.0:30:00.47.Default..0.0.0..THAT HAPPENED.\NNOW THAT YOU SAID IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:00.49.0:30:01.74.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:01.76.0:30:04.87.Default..0.0.0..I AM ASKING SOMEONE\NWITH A GOOD GRACIOUS
Dialogue: 0.0:30:04.90.0:30:06.14.Default..0.0.0..TO GO FUCKING CLEAN\NTHAT BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:06.17.0:30:07.18.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT TOUCHING IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:07.20.0:30:08.61.Default..0.0.0..I CLEANED IT\NFIVE TIMES ALREADY.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:08.64.0:30:11.05.Default..0.0.0..AND WHILE YOU'RE AT IT.\NHIT THE COMMUNITY BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.07.0:30:12.95.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. WORD.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:12.97.0:30:14.02.Default..0.0.0..BUSTED.\NME?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:14.04.0:30:15.39.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NSOMEONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:15.41.0:30:17.12.Default..0.0.0..TO BE HONEST WITH YOU.\NI FEEL BAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:17.14.0:30:18.92.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I HAVEN'T\NWASHED A DISH YET.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:18.95.0:30:20.46.Default..0.0.0..I HAVEN'T CLEANED\NSHIT YET.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:20.48.0:30:21.69.Default..0.0.0..EXCEPT MY ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:21.72.0:30:24.06.Default..0.0.0..SO I THINK THIS IS THE TIME\NFOR ME TO STEP UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:24.08.0:30:25.25.Default..0.0.0..SO I DECIDE TO DO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:27.72.0:30:29.70.Default..0.0.0..♪ OOH. I CAN FEEL IT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:29.72.0:30:31.30.Default..0.0.0..♪ LET ME SHOW YOU THE WAY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:31.33.0:30:32.77.Default..0.0.0..POOP. AAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:32.79.0:30:35.04.Default..0.0.0..♪ THE SMELL OF COOL WIND ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:35.06.0:30:36.44.Default..0.0.0..MAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:36.46.0:30:38.61.Default..0.0.0..♪ JUST LOVIN' THE PLACE\NI'M IN ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:38.63.0:30:40.54.Default..0.0.0..OHH. POOP STAINS!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.57.0:30:41.98.Default..0.0.0..♪ TAKE JUST A MINUTE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:42.00.0:30:43.78.Default..0.0.0..♪ TO DIG RIGHT IN IT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:43.80.0:30:46.98.Default..0.0.0..♪ DIG RIGHT INTO\NALL THE LOVE YOU BRING ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:47.01.0:30:50.85.Default..0.0.0..♪ JUST LIE BACK AND WATCH IT\NALL GO RIGHT ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:30:50.88.0:30:53.02.Default..0.0.0..AAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:53.05.0:30:54.19.Default..0.0.0..NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:57.92.0:30:59.53.Default..0.0.0..HERE. IN BETWEEN\NHIS SHEETS.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:59.55.0:31:01.30.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. WE GOT YOU.\NMOTHERFUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:01.32.0:31:03.37.Default..0.0.0..UGH. I HAD THAT CHICK\NOVER THE OTHER NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:03.39.0:31:04.40.Default..0.0.0..BAD VAGINA?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:04.42.0:31:05.54.Default..0.0.0..IT SMELLED\NLIKE GRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:05.56.0:31:07.60.Default..0.0.0..THE CHEESE BED\NIS THE BEST PRANK.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:07.63.0:31:08.73.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A SUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:19.67.0:31:21.22.Default..0.0.0..FOR ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:21.24.0:31:22.92.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:22.94.0:31:24.09.Default..0.0.0..I MADE MAD SHIT TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:24.11.0:31:27.26.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE ONES I WANTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:27.28.0:31:29.93.Default..0.0.0..RONNIE. DEFINITELY\NI FEEL LIKE IS REFORMED.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:29.95.0:31:31.09.Default..0.0.0..I. LIKE. LOVE TALKING TO HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:31.12.0:31:32.43.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE BEING WITH HIM NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:32.45.0:31:34.33.Default..0.0.0..JUST BECAUSE HE'S HAPPY\NAND HE'S DIFFERENT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:34.35.0:31:35.60.Default..0.0.0..HE'S CHANGED.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.62.0:31:38.10.Default..0.0.0..GET YOUR BUTT UP. PLEASE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:38.13.0:31:39.40.Default..0.0.0..SNOOK. YOU STAYING HOME?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:39.43.0:31:40.50.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:40.53.0:31:42.74.Default..0.0.0..LET'S DO SOMETHING ELSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:42.76.0:31:45.07.Default..0.0.0..LIKE WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.10.0:31:46.64.Default..0.0.0..THINK WE'RE ALL JUST\NGONNA BE SOBER...
Dialogue: 0.0:31:46.67.0:31:48.11.Default..0.0.0..AND HANG OUT TONIGHT\NFOR THE. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:48.14.0:31:49.40.Default..0.0.0..THE FIRST TIME ALL SUMMER.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:54.71.0:31:57.72.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GET VIRGIN MARGARITAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.75.0:32:00.06.Default..0.0.0..I ACTUALLY LIKE\NNOT GOING TO THE BAR. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:00.08.0:32:02.93.Default..0.0.0..SO ME. RON. AND SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:02.95.0:32:04.09.Default..0.0.0..TEAM SOBER TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:04.12.0:32:05.80.Default..0.0.0..WE WANNA DO SOMETHING FUN.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.82.0:32:08.47.Default..0.0.0..SO WE DECIDED\NTO GO TO BEACH BAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:08.49.0:32:09.57.Default..0.0.0..CRICKET.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:09.59.0:32:11.17.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S NOBODY HERE!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:11.19.0:32:12.87.Default..0.0.0..OH. NO.\NOH. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:12.89.0:32:14.10.Default..0.0.0..COOL!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.13.0:32:16.71.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO WAKE UP\NAND NOT HAVE A HANGOVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:16.73.0:32:18.84.Default..0.0.0..AND. YOU KNOW WHAT. I CAN HAVE\NA GOOD TIME WITHOUT DRINKING.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.87.0:32:20.94.Default..0.0.0..SO. YOU KNOW.\NFUCK YOU. ALCOHOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:20.97.0:32:22.51.Default..0.0.0..HI. SOMETHING TO DRINK\NWHILE YOU'RE LOOKING?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.54.0:32:24.95.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE HAVE\NTHREE TEQUILAS?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:24.97.0:32:26.02.Default..0.0.0..I'M JUST KIDDING.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:26.04.0:32:28.02.Default..0.0.0..NO. NO. NO. NO.\NI WILL...
Dialogue: 0.0:32:28.04.0:32:29.80.Default..0.0.0..YAY. SHOULD HAVE SEEN\NYOUR EYEBALLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:33.11.0:32:35.69.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD. THIS IS GONNA\NBE A HORRIBLE TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:35.72.0:32:38.13.Default..0.0.0..THE WEATHER IN SEASIDE TONIGHT\NIS PRETTY DREARY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:38.15.0:32:40.23.Default..0.0.0..BUT WE'RE ALL GOING\NTO AZTEC TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:40.25.0:32:41.46.Default..0.0.0..HOPEFULLY. THERE'S\NA COUPLE HOT CHICKS
Dialogue: 0.0:32:41.49.0:32:42.83.Default..0.0.0..AND GOOD MUSIC PUMPING.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:42.86.0:32:44.03.Default..0.0.0..AND WE'RE GONNA HAVE\NA GOOD TIME TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:47.06.0:32:51.37.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:32:51.40.0:32:54.41.Default..0.0.0..I'M GAY.\NSHE'S MY GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:54.43.0:32:57.65.Default..0.0.0..FOR REAL?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:57.67.0:32:59.65.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU FULLY GAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:59.67.0:33:01.42.Default..0.0.0..NO.\NAWESOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.88.0:33:03.94.Default..0.0.0..OH. THERE HE IS.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.41.0:33:08.49.Default..0.0.0..YOU LOOK GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:08.52.0:33:10.86.Default..0.0.0..I HAVEN'T SEEN ROGER\NFOR A WHILE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:10.88.0:33:12.96.Default..0.0.0..UM. I WAS JUST...\NREAL EXCITED TO SEE HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:12.99.0:33:13.96.Default..0.0.0..HE'S SO CUTE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:13.99.0:33:15.47.Default..0.0.0..CHEERS.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:15.49.0:33:17.40.Default..0.0.0..CHEERS.\NSO WHAT ELSE?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:17.42.0:33:19.47.Default..0.0.0..NOTHING.\NWHAT'D I MISS?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:19.49.0:33:21.77.Default..0.0.0..I WENT SPRAY TANNING\NNAKED TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:21.80.0:33:23.94.Default..0.0.0..SO AM I GOING TO GET\NALL ORANGE LATER?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:23.96.0:33:25.98.Default..0.0.0..I TOOK A SHOWER.\NOH.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:26.00.0:33:28.48.Default..0.0.0..I WAS WORRIED ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:28.50.0:33:29.87.Default..0.0.0..RUBBING OFF ON YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:33.07.0:33:34.42.Default..0.0.0..HOW OLD ARE YOU?\N21.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:34.44.0:33:36.02.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE 21?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:36.04.0:33:38.45.Default..0.0.0..WANNA SEE MY I.D.?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:38.48.0:33:39.89.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS WHEN\NMY HAIR WAS BLONDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:39.91.0:33:42.02.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\N21. YOU'RE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:42.05.0:33:43.81.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:47.62.0:33:49.53.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. SO WHAT ARE WE\NGONNA GET MIKE BACK WITH?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:49.56.0:33:51.33.Default..0.0.0..FART ON HIS PILLOW!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:51.36.0:33:52.57.Default..0.0.0..SO. LIKE YOU COULD\NFART ON HIS PILLOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:52.59.0:33:53.67.Default..0.0.0..SO HE GETS PINK EYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:53.69.0:33:55.50.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE MIKE LOVES PRANKS\NSO MUCH...
Dialogue: 0.0:33:55.53.0:33:57.31.Default..0.0.0..SENDING ME TO THE CITY.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:57.33.0:34:00.01.Default..0.0.0..LAST YEAR PUTTING SHIT\NUNDER VINNY'S BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:00.03.0:34:02.68.Default..0.0.0..WHY DON'T YOU GET A TASTE\NOF YOUR OWN MEDICINE. MICHAEL?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:02.70.0:34:05.58.Default..0.0.0..LET'S OPEN UP THE FRIDGE\NAND SEE WHAT WE'VE GOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:05.61.0:34:06.92.Default..0.0.0..LET'S SEE WHAT WE'RE\NWORKING WITH HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:06.94.0:34:09.05.Default..0.0.0..CREAM CHEESE.\NGRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:09.08.0:34:11.35.Default..0.0.0..THAT'LL DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:11.38.0:34:13.12.Default..0.0.0..SO ME. SNOOK. AND SAM\NARE GONNA GO UPSTAIRS
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.15.0:34:14.66.Default..0.0.0..AND PRANK HIS BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:19.59.0:34:21.16.Default..0.0.0..OOH.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.19.0:34:23.20.Default..0.0.0..LOOKS LIKE A PIZZA.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.22.0:34:25.00.Default..0.0.0..SHOULD I ADD\NSOME CREAM CHEESE?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:31.16.0:34:33.01.Default..0.0.0..SMEAR IT INTO HIS SHEET.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:34.23.0:34:35.81.Default..0.0.0..HE DOESN'T WASH\NHIS SHEETS ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:35.84.0:34:37.61.Default..0.0.0..SO HE'S NEVER GONNA FIND IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.64.0:34:39.58.Default..0.0.0..AND WE JUST STARTED MAKING\NA NICE SMORGASBORD
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.61.0:34:41.62.Default..0.0.0..OF ALL KINDS OF CHEESE\NAND RED PEPPER.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:41.64.0:34:44.75.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S FOR SENDING ME\NTO NEW YORK. MOTHERFUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.72.0:34:54.53.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT'S LIKE THE SEALING\NTO THE WHOLE JOKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:55.69.0:34:57.93.Default..0.0.0..YOU GOT CHEESED.\NOLD CHEESY BASTARD.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:57.96.0:34:59.57.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. IT'S GONNA STINK.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:59.59.0:35:02.24.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. WE GOT YOU.\NMOTHERFUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:02.26.0:35:03.51.Default..0.0.0..OH. WE GOT YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:03.53.0:35:06.11.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS FOR SENDING ME\NTO NEW YORK. YOU FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:06.13.0:35:07.18.Default..0.0.0..YOUR FACE.\NCREAM CH...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:09.64.0:35:11.51.Default..0.0.0..TEAM SOBER. BITCH!\NOHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:11.54.0:35:13.35.Default..0.0.0..BOOYAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:17.08.0:35:19.42.Default..0.0.0..I THINK YOU'RE HOT.\NBUT YOU WANNA DO YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.45.0:35:21.29.Default..0.0.0..I'M HAPPY WHERE I AM.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:21.31.0:35:22.86.Default..0.0.0..PROMISE?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.88.0:35:24.09.Default..0.0.0..PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:24.12.0:35:26.40.Default..0.0.0..PROMISE?\NPROMISE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:26.42.0:35:29.13.Default..0.0.0..I PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.16.0:35:30.97.Default..0.0.0..MY GIRL IS 100% D.T.F.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:30.99.0:35:34.24.Default..0.0.0..WHEN DO YOU GO HOME?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:34.26.0:35:37.17.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT'S IT.\NSO ADD ME TO THE SMUSH BOARD.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.20.0:35:38.17.Default..0.0.0..I GOT A HOT CHICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:38.20.0:35:39.48.Default..0.0.0..BRINGING HER TO THE BEDROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:39.50.0:35:40.77.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M GETTING IT IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:43.50.0:35:45.24.Default..0.0.0..HELLO? PAULY?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:48.31.0:35:49.82.Default..0.0.0..BOO BOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:49.84.0:35:51.19.Default..0.0.0..WE ALL KNOW ROGER.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:51.21.0:35:53.26.Default..0.0.0..WANNA SEE MY DUCK PHONE?\NRIGHT THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:53.28.0:35:55.83.Default..0.0.0..HI. DEE.\NTHIS IS SAMMI.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:55.85.0:35:57.19.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS RONNIE.\NTHIS IS SNOOKI.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:57.22.0:35:58.50.Default..0.0.0..HI.\NTHIS IS BLAIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:58.52.0:36:00.02.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS BLAIR.\NTHIS IS BLAIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:01.72.0:36:02.87.Default..0.0.0..IS THAT IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:02.89.0:36:04.33.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW.\NBUT IT LOOKS GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.36.0:36:06.67.Default..0.0.0..WHAT UP?\NHELLO.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:06.69.0:36:07.97.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S SNOOKI.\NHI!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:08.00.0:36:09.97.Default..0.0.0..HI.\NTHAT'S SAMMI.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:10.00.0:36:11.41.Default..0.0.0..HI.\NWHAT IS... WHAT IS...
Dialogue: 0.0:36:11.43.0:36:12.91.Default..0.0.0..WHAT ARE WE DOING\NTO OURSELVES?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:12.93.0:36:15.11.Default..0.0.0..LET THEM DO THEIR THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:15.14.0:36:17.05.Default..0.0.0..UM... PROBABLY\NGONNA HAVE ICE TEA.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:17.07.0:36:18.78.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS FUN.\NI USED TO LOVE THAT GAME.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:18.81.0:36:19.88.Default..0.0.0..ME TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:19.91.0:36:21.25.Default..0.0.0..YOU WANT WATER?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:21.27.0:36:22.49.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:22.51.0:36:24.59.Default..0.0.0..MY NIPPLES WON'T STAY\NIN MY SHIRT.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:27.31.0:36:29.75.Default..0.0.0..THEIR BEER GOGGLES\NARE TERRIBLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:35.12.0:36:36.60.Default..0.0.0..SCARES ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:36.62.0:36:37.93.Default..0.0.0..YOU WANT SOME\NCOMFORTABLE STUFF?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.96.0:36:39.80.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. GOOD IDEA.\NPUT THESE ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:39.83.0:36:41.74.Default..0.0.0..OH. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:41.76.0:36:42.79.Default..0.0.0..THE CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.40.0:36:47.21.Default..0.0.0..WILL YOU SHUT THE LIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:47.23.0:36:48.88.Default..0.0.0..THEY'RE BOTH GOING\NTO GET PINK EYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:48.90.0:36:50.57.Default..0.0.0..GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.94.0:36:58.82.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S GROSS.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:58.85.0:37:00.56.Default..0.0.0..SMELLS LIKE GARBAGE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:00.58.0:37:02.13.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.15.0:37:04.46.Default..0.0.0..SPEAKING OF SMELL. UGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.48.0:37:06.13.Default..0.0.0..I HAD THAT CHICK OVER\NTHE OTHER NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.15.0:37:07.70.Default..0.0.0..UGH.\NEW!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:07.72.0:37:09.83.Default..0.0.0..I HAD TO KICK HER OUT.\NWHAT SMELL WAS IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:09.86.0:37:12.13.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS OBVIOUSLY HER.\NYOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:12.16.0:37:13.30.Default..0.0.0..BAD VAGINA?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:13.33.0:37:15.37.Default..0.0.0..IT SMELLED LIKE FUCKIN'\NGRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:15.40.0:37:17.34.Default..0.0.0..OHH.\NAND... BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.36.0:37:18.37.Default..0.0.0..LIKE A SUSHI MARKET?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:18.40.0:37:19.38.Default..0.0.0..NO. BUT NO. IT DIDN'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:19.40.0:37:20.74.Default..0.0.0..IT JUST SMELLED\NLIKE GRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:20.77.0:37:22.31.Default..0.0.0..AND I WAS LIKE.\N"WHAT IS THAT SMELL?"
Dialogue: 0.0:37:22.34.0:37:23.65.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S LIKE. "DO YOU WANT YOUR\NCLOTHES BACK?"
Dialogue: 0.0:37:23.67.0:37:24.85.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE. "NO. YOU CAN\NKEEP THE CLOTHES."
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.87.0:37:25.88.Default..0.0.0..GRATED CHEESE?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:25.91.0:37:27.38.Default..0.0.0..I THINK THE CHEESE BED
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.41.0:37:30.69.Default..0.0.0..IS THE BEST PRANK\NIN{\i1} JERSEY SHORE{\i0} HISTORY.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:30.71.0:37:33.96.Default..0.0.0..JUST BECAUSE NO ONE EVER\NPRANKED MIKE LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:33.98.0:37:36.03.Default..0.0.0..AND THE FACT THAT HE THINKS\NIT'S A GRENADE...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:36.05.0:37:38.33.Default..0.0.0..GRENADE'S VAGINA SMELLING\NLIKE CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:38.35.0:37:39.83.Default..0.0.0..WHEN. REALLY.\NIT'S YOUR FRICKIN' BED
Dialogue: 0.0:37:39.85.0:37:41.56.Default..0.0.0..SMELLING LIKE CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:41.59.0:37:42.66.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A SUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:42.69.0:37:43.69.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A SUCKER. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.83.0:37:46.50.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NHE GOT A GIRL OVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:46.53.0:37:47.84.Default..0.0.0..AND HE GOES. "I COULDN'T\NHOOK UP WITH HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:47.86.0:37:50.34.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE SHE SMELLED LIKE\NGRATED CHEESE."
Dialogue: 0.0:37:51.56.0:37:53.14.Default..0.0.0..IT IS SO EXTREMELY SATISFYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:53.17.0:37:56.58.Default..0.0.0..KNOWING THAT WE GOT. LIKE.\NTHE ULTIMATE PRANKER HIMSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:59.17.0:38:00.25.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S GROSS.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:00.27.0:38:01.68.Default..0.0.0..THIS PRANK\NIS FRIGGIN' FABULOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:01.71.0:38:03.65.Default..0.0.0..SHE LEFT. I HAD TO SPRAY\NMY BED WITH AXE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.68.0:38:06.22.Default..0.0.0..AND THEY SMELLED HORRIBLE.\NI DIDN'T KNOW WHAT IT WAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:06.25.0:38:08.22.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE. "YO. IT SMELLS LIKE\NGRATED CHEESE RIGHT NOW."
Dialogue: 0.0:38:08.25.0:38:10.79.Default..0.0.0..SO THEN SHE GAVE ME {bleep}.\NAND SHE WAS DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:10.82.0:38:13.03.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M LIKE. "YO. I GOT YOUR\NTAXI READY OUTSIDE."
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.05.0:38:14.16.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:14.19.0:38:16.07.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN GET AN S.T.D.\NFROM THAT. YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:16.09.0:38:17.20.Default..0.0.0..S.T.D. FROM WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:17.22.0:38:18.87.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN'T GET\NAN S.T.D. FROM THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:18.89.0:38:20.97.Default..0.0.0..YES. YOU CAN!\NTHAT'S A BIG WAY TO GET ONE!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.99.0:38:24.77.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN GET IT... YOU CAN\NGET SOMETHING FROM {bleep}?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:24.80.0:38:26.24.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T THINK YOU'RE CORRECT.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:26.27.0:38:27.61.Default..0.0.0..WOULD YOU LIKE TO CALL\NTHAT DOCTOR IN THERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:27.63.0:38:31.81.Default..0.0.0..MIKE IS SO DUMB WHEN IT COMES\NTO SAFE SEX AND S.T.D.s.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.84.0:38:33.38.Default..0.0.0..I'M CALLING THE DOCTOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:33.41.0:38:35.25.Default..0.0.0..WE HAVE A DOCTOR IN THE BOOK.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:35.27.0:38:36.29.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:36.31.0:38:37.49.Default..0.0.0..THIS GOES BACK\NTO FIFTH GRADE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:37.51.0:38:38.89.Default..0.0.0..LIKE SEX EDUCATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:38.91.0:38:40.66.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAVE TO PRACTICE\NSAFE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:40.68.0:38:43.63.Default..0.0.0..WHAT HAPPENS WHEN SOMETHING\NSMELLS LIKE GRATED CHEESE?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:43.65.0:38:45.49.Default..0.0.0..NO. WE'RE GONNA ALSO FIND OUT\NIF YOU CATCH...
Dialogue: 0.0:38:45.52.0:38:47.10.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?\NHI. HOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:47.12.0:38:48.13.Default..0.0.0..HOW ARE YOU?\NGRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:48.15.0:38:50.20.Default..0.0.0..MY ROOMMATES\NWOULD LIKE TO KNOW
Dialogue: 0.0:38:50.22.0:38:53.04.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU CAN STILL CATCH\NA SEXUALLY TRANSMITTED DISEASE
Dialogue: 0.0:38:53.06.0:38:55.74.Default..0.0.0..WITHOUT USING A CONDOM\NIF ONE OF MY GUYS IN THE HOUSE
Dialogue: 0.0:38:55.76.0:38:58.77.Default..0.0.0..GOT... ORAL... PLEASURE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:58.80.0:39:00.34.Default..0.0.0..CERTAIN ONES. YES.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:00.37.0:39:02.81.Default..0.0.0..USUALLY THE MAIN ONE THAT'S\NCONTAGIOUS THAT WAY IS HERPES.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:02.84.0:39:05.35.Default..0.0.0..THE MAIN ONE THAT'S CONTAGIOUS\NTHAT WAY IS HERPES.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:05.37.0:39:06.75.Default..0.0.0..UCK!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.77.0:39:09.22.Default..0.0.0..AND WE ALSO HAD\NA WOMAN COME IN HERE
Dialogue: 0.0:39:09.24.0:39:12.02.Default..0.0.0..THAT HAD A SMELL LIKE...\NGRATED CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:12.05.0:39:14.66.Default..0.0.0..GRATED CHEESE. DOES\NTHAT MEAN SHE HAD A. UM...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.68.0:39:16.16.Default..0.0.0..YEAST INFECTION.\NYEAST INFECTION?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:16.18.0:39:17.93.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. POSSIBLY. YEAH.\NYES. POSSIBLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.95.0:39:20.13.Default..0.0.0..All: OHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:20.15.0:39:22.07.Default..0.0.0..IT WON'T BE LONG BEFORE\NMIKE'S DICK FALLS OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:22.09.0:39:23.93.Default..0.0.0..WOW. SHE REALLY\NLEFT HER MARK.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:23.96.0:39:25.43.Default..0.0.0..OH. YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:25.46.0:39:27.07.Default..0.0.0..I JUST GOT {bleep}.\NTHAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:27.09.0:39:28.44.Default..0.0.0..I DID MAKE OUT WITH HER...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:28.46.0:39:30.17.Default..0.0.0..WHICH MEANS YOU PROBABLY\NMIGHT GET SOME YEAST IN YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:39.21.0:39:41.58.Default..0.0.0..HI. DEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:41.61.0:39:43.82.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU GOING OUT?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:43.84.0:39:45.69.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO APOLOGIZE
Dialogue: 0.0:39:45.71.0:39:48.49.Default..0.0.0..IF I SAID. LIKE. FUCKED UP\NSHIT TO YOU THE OTHER NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:48.52.0:39:49.86.Default..0.0.0..I WAS REALLY DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.88.0:39:51.36.Default..0.0.0..MM-HMM.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:51.38.0:39:53.13.Default..0.0.0..AND IF I WAS. LIKE.\NMAD STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:53.15.0:39:55.60.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS UPSETTING ME.\NI DIDN'T WANT YOU TO CRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:55.62.0:39:58.57.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUT YOU KNOW\NI CAN'T LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.59.0:40:00.00.Default..0.0.0..I JUST DON'T WANT\NANYTHING TO. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:00.03.0:40:01.30.Default..0.0.0..CHANGE BETWEEN\NOUR FRIENDSHIP.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:01.33.0:40:02.57.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU KNOW I LOVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:02.60.0:40:04.37.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT YOU\NTO CRY LIKE THAT ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:04.40.0:40:06.74.Default..0.0.0..MY BAD.\NNOT BECAUSE OF ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:06.77.0:40:07.94.Default..0.0.0..BUT BECAUSE OF ANYTHING.\NYOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:07.97.0:40:09.38.Default..0.0.0..YOU WERE. LIKE. HYSTERICAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:09.40.0:40:11.01.Default..0.0.0..LIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:11.04.0:40:12.18.Default..0.0.0..STOP!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:12.21.0:40:13.55.Default..0.0.0..LIKE ONE OF THOSE CRIES.\NLIKE...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:13.57.0:40:15.65.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. EMBARRASSING.\NCOOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:15.68.0:40:19.09.Default..0.0.0..SO I CAN KEEP ON\NSMASHING GIRLS?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:19.11.0:40:21.06.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NI JUST DON'T WANNA SEE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:21.08.0:40:23.23.Default..0.0.0..AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:23.25.0:40:24.59.Default..0.0.0..ASSHOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:29.19.0:40:37.13.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
